satellite/000501/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet outdoor area with a mix of paved paths and natural landscapes. In the center, a large patch of brown earth is split by light-colored curved paths that resemble a stylized number or symbol. To the left, a paved section with dark rectangular shapes, possibly benches or planters, is surrounded by greenery. On the right, more green trees and bushes form a natural border. The area appears calm and well-organized, possibly a park or garden space. The image is clear, with even lighting, suggesting a cloudless day and good visibility. The overall atmosphere is peaceful and structured, with no signs of people or activity.

satellite/000501/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet residential area with a mix of green spaces and paved roads. At the center, a large patch of brown, bare soil stretches out, possibly a vacant lot or a field under development. Curved white lines cut through the soil, likely paths or what remains of old concrete structures. To the left, a block of buildings with light-colored walls stands in a neat row, separated by narrow walkways. A cluster of dark green trees lies between these buildings and the open field, providing a natural border. On the right, more trees form a dense green edge, adding depth to the scene. Below, another building with a dark roof is partially visible, surrounded by foliage. The sky is overcast, casting even, soft light over the area, which gives the image a calm and still atmosphere. There is no movement or activity evident, suggesting a peaceful moment in a suburban neighborhood. The overall impression is one of quiet order, with nature and development coexisting without conflict.

satellite/000501/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a mixed urban and green space, showing a combination of built structures and open land. In the center of the image is a large brown patch of bare earth, possibly a construction site or vacant lot, crossed by two curved white paths that create a Y-shaped division. To the right of the dirt area lies a dense strip of green trees forming a natural border. On the left side are several buildings with flat roofs, including a long rectangular structure, possibly a school or warehouse, and a small construction site with excavated holes and marked lanes. A paved road runs horizontally across the top of the image, with a white striped wall (likely a barrier) on its edge. The scene appears overcast, with soft lighting and no shadows, suggesting cloudy weather. The area gives a sense of organized urban planning with a mix of development and nature, though the unused land contrasts sharply with the surrounding structured layout. There are no people visible, lending a quiet, still atmosphere to the scene.

satellite/000502/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet residential area. In the center, a patch of dark green trees and bushes covers the ground, partially shading a narrow path that curves through a grassy field. To the left, a light-colored building with a flat roof sits beside a small area of paved ground. On the right, a dirt path drops gently down a slope, heading toward a large structure with a slanted, weathered roof. The scene is calm and still, with no people or vehicles visible. The sky is bright but overcast, casting soft shadows and giving the area a muted, peaceful tone. The details are slightly blurry, likely due to the image resolution and the distance from the camera. The overall impression is one of quiet, unchanging everyday life in a subdued neighborhood.

satellite/000502/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural landscape with a mix of agricultural fields and forested areas. In the center, a winding dirt path curves through the ground, dividing the brown plowed fields on the right from a small wooded section on the left. To the lower left, a cluster of trees and bushes surrounds a simple, low-rise building with a dark roof, suggesting a farm structure or small house. On the upper left, another building with a flat roof is partially visible, surrounded by what appears to be a paved lot. A dense, green patch of trees lies beneath the road, forming a natural corridor. The overall scene is quiet and undisturbed, with no signs of human activity. The image appears to be taken on a clear day, with ample sunlight illuminating the landscape. Shadows are soft and orderly, indicating the sun is high in the sky. The colors are earthy and natural—browns, greens, and grays—giving the area a calm and tranquil feel. Overall, the scene evokes a sense of peaceful rural life, untouched by urban development.

satellite/000502/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with a mix of buildings and open land. In the lower part of the image, there is a large building with a flat roof, possibly a house or a small community center, surrounded by green trees. To the left, there is another structure with a beige roof and a smaller courtyard area with a patterned fence and a few bushes. A few curved pathways cross a large strip of bare soil or dirt in the middle of the image, suggesting a park or a vacant lot. The upper right section shows more planted greenery, possibly a garden or landscaped area. There are no people or moving vehicles visible, giving the scene a calm and still appearance. The lighting suggests a clear day with bright overhead sunlight, casting sharp shadows. The overall atmosphere feels peaceful and quiet, without signs of urban activity. The colors are natural and earthy—greens, browns, and grays dominate, adding to the tranquil and orderly look of the area.

satellite/000503/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural landscape, featuring a dirt path that curves through the center of the frame. On the lower left, a building with a dark roof sits near a cluster of green trees, suggesting a small structure like a shed or cabin. To the right, a gravel clearing borders the path, with more trees scattered around. The land above the path is mostly open and bare, showing brownish soil, while the surrounding vegetation is lush and dense in spots. The image appears to be taken on a bright day with clear visibility, capturing a calm and quiet area. The overall scene feels peaceful and isolated, with no signs of human activity.

satellite/000503/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural landscape featuring a large open field with light-colored paths forming geometric patterns across dark brown soil. In the lower left, there is a dark rectangular structure that looks like a building with a flat roof, surrounded by dense green trees. To the left of the field, a smaller paved area with a few objects is visible, possibly a parking space or enclosure. The right side of the image shows more lush vegetation, with trees extending into the upper edge. The paths through the field appear well-maintained, forming curved lines that lead toward the center. The overall atmosphere is calm and quiet, with no signs of activity or people. The weather seems clear and bright, as the landscape is evenly lit with no shadows indicating rain, fog, or heavy cloud cover. The scene has a peaceful and undisturbed feeling, typical of a countryside setting during daylight.

satellite/000503/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a park-like area with open fields and pathways. In the center is a large patch of bare brown earth, divided by curved dirt paths that move like quiet rivers through the space. To the left of the central field, there is a dense area of green trees, some arranged in a grid-like pattern, possibly a garden or orchard. On the right, more greenery appears, with scattered trees and shrubs forming a natural border. Below the central field, there is a long building with a flat roof and light-colored walls, possibly a pavilion or rest area, surrounded by trees and walkways. To the lower left, a paved surface with a symmetrical pattern suggests a plaza or car parking area. The scene is lit by bright, even sunlight, creating soft shadows and highlighting the textures of the grass, dirt, and pavement. The atmosphere is calm and peaceful, with a sense of order and stillness, like a quiet corner in a city where nature meets structure. There are no people or vehicles visible, adding to the quiet mood.

satellite/000504/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural area with a mix of open land and vegetation. In the lower left, there is a building with a flat roof, possibly a shed or small house, surrounded by green bushes and trees. A white path curves around the area, forming a small loop in the upper part of the image. To the right, a dense patch of trees covers a small hill. The ground appears brown and dry, possibly farmland or an unused field. The image has a slightly dark tone, suggesting it was taken under overcast or cloudy conditions. There is no visible movement or people, giving the scene a still and calm atmosphere. The colors are muted, with shades of green, brown, and gray dominating.

satellite/000504/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural landscape featuring large, open fields separated by narrow dirt paths and patches of trees. In the lower left corner, a dark rectangular building with a flat roof stands near a light-colored structure, possibly a shed or enclosure, surrounded by greenery. To the right, dense clusters of trees form small groves, contrasting with the bare, earthy tones of the fields. A network of curving white paths cuts through the scene, connecting the different areas and suggesting routes for walking or farming activity. The terrain appears flat and undisturbed, with no signs of heavy human activity. The lighting is even and diffuse, indicating an overcast day with no strong shadows. The image has a quiet, calm tone, evoking the stillness of a country area in a quiet season. There is no visible movement, making the scene feel peaceful and empty, almost like a quiet corner of the countryside.

satellite/000504/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a park or garden area with walking paths. The central object is a series of light-colored, curved paths that split and connect across a large area of bare earth, creating a geometric pattern. To the left, there is a dark green patch of dense trees and shrubs, and at the bottom left, a small structure with a flat roof and white walls is visible, possibly a shelter or building. Green bushes and trees surround the paths on all sides, especially along the edges, giving a natural border. Roads or paved sections can be seen at the top and right edges, introducing man-made elements. The overall scene is quiet and orderly, captured in daylight with clear visibility. There is no sign of rain or fog, and the sky appears neutral. The atmosphere is calm and simple, with natural and constructed forms merging in a peaceful arrangement. The image shows a quiet, regular outdoor space suitable for walking or relaxation.

satellite/000505/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural landscape featuring a curved road that splits into two paths. The central object is a wide, light-colored road with a gentle curve, surrounded by brown fields, likely farmland or plowed soil. To the lower left, there is a patch of dense green trees and a small structure, possibly a building or shed. The area appears open and flat, with no visible people or vehicles, giving it a quiet and still atmosphere. The road contrasts sharply with the darker ground, making its shape clear and prominent. The image seems taken on a clear day, as the details are sharp and there is no fog or cloud cover. The overall impression is calm and unpopulated, with a sense of simplicity and isolation.

satellite/000505/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural landscape with unpaved roads cutting through open land. The central feature is a network of curved dirt paths that divide the area into several large, unplanted sections of bare earth, showing a slightly uneven surface. On the left side of the image, a dense patch of dark green trees contrasts with the brown ground, forming a natural boundary. A small building with a gray roof and white walls is visible in the lower-left corner, partially covered by trees. The path winding through the center leads toward the lower right, where it appears to connect to a wider, straight road. There are no people or vehicles visible. The lighting is even and bright, suggesting a clear day with no clouds or shadows. The overall atmosphere is calm and empty, with no signs of human activity. The image has no color variation beyond earth tones and green, giving it a quiet and isolated feel.

satellite/000505/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, open outdoor area with several dirt paths forming a network across a grassy and bare land space. In the center, there is a wide, curved path that divides the space into sections, with smaller paths branching off in different directions. To the left, a dense patch of green trees and bushes contrasts with the brown, exposed soil. Below that, a rectangular building with a dark roof sits near the edge of the land, partially hidden from view. On the right side, more open land stretches out, with a few narrow walkways leading toward the perimeter. The area appears quiet and unused, with no visible people or vehicles. The lighting is even and bright, suggesting a clear sky with no clouds, creating a calm and still atmosphere across the scene. The colors are mostly earthy—browns and greens—giving the image a natural and subdued tone. It looks like a park or recreation ground under development or not currently in use.

satellite/000506/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural landscape showing a winding road that splits into two paths. The road cuts through a large, flat area covered with dry brown grass and patches of bare earth. On the left side, there is a dense cluster of green trees forming a small wooded area. The road appears light in color, possibly made of dirt or gravel, and its curves stand out against the darker surroundings. The overall scene is quiet and still, with no visible movement or signs of people. The sky is clear, and the lighting suggests a calm, sunny day with no clouds or fog. The image gives a sense of isolation and peacefulness, typical of a remote countryside setting.

satellite/000506/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural landscape, showing a large open field with a dirt path that splits into several branching trails. The central area is mostly flat and covered in dry brown soil, suggesting it is either fallow or recently plowed. On the left side, a patch of dense green trees provides contrast to the otherwise bare terrain. A smaller, curved path separates the wooded area from the main field. On the right, the larger portion of the field stretches out, with fewer visible details due to the distance and angle. The paths appear light-colored, possibly made of gravel or packed earth. The image has a muted tone, with no strong shadows, indicating a cloudy or overcast day. The overall atmosphere is calm and quiet, with no signs of people or vehicles, giving the scene a peaceful and untouched feel. The edges of the field are less defined, blending into natural surroundings. A few faint lines along the top edge suggest a boundary like a fence or hedge. The image lacks bright colors or dramatic lighting, reinforcing a sense of stillness and simplicity.

satellite/000506/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural landscape featuring a network of curved dirt paths dividing open fields. The central area consists of large brown plots of land, likely farmland or undeveloped ground, with the paths forming a gentle, winding pattern through them. To the left, there is a dense patch of green trees and shrubs, creating a natural border. Smaller green spaces and a few isolated trees are scattered around the edges. The overall scene appears calm and quiet, with a sense of stillness under bright, clear daylight. There are no signs of people or vehicles, which enhances the peaceful and isolated atmosphere. The image has a slightly hazy quality, possibly due to sunlight reflection or minimal atmospheric dust. The contrast between the brown earth and green vegetation is subtle but noticeable, giving the land a natural, unspoiled look. The overall impression is one of quiet rural simplicity, with the paths suggesting a quiet place for walking or agricultural work.

satellite/000507/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural landscape with a network of narrow roads cutting through open land. The central focus is a white, curving road that splits into two branches, forming a Y-shape across the brownish terrain. To the left, a small patch of green trees borders the road, suggesting a forested or wooded area. The surrounding fields appear dry and barren, with no signs of buildings or vehicles. The image was taken on a clear day, with bright sunlight casting soft shadows that enhance the texture of the ground. The atmosphere is calm and still, with no movement or activity visible. The overall mood is quiet and isolated, reflecting a remote, undeveloped area.

satellite/000507/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural landscape with several large, unvegetated fields separated by winding dirt paths. The central area features a large, dark brown field bordered by a light-colored curved path that splits into two sections, forming a T-shape. To the lower left, a dense cluster of green trees and shrubs contrasts with the open land. A narrow dirt road runs diagonally from the lower center toward the left edge, intersecting with another path near the upper right. The terrain appears dry and flat, with patches of uneven, dark soil scattered throughout the fields. The lighting in the image is bright and even, suggesting a clear day with no visible clouds or rain. The overall scene is quiet and empty, presenting a calm and unpopulated area with no signs of human activity or structures. The lack of buildings or vehicles contributes to a sense of isolation and tranquility. The land appears prepared for farming or development, though currently unused. The image captures a peaceful, still atmosphere typical of undeveloped rural space.

satellite/000507/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural landscape featuring a large, open area with several dirt paths winding through it. The central part of the image shows a wide, brown field, likely recently plowed or cleared, with patches of darker soil suggesting recent activity. The paths form a network, curving around the field and connecting to the edges of the frame, where dense green vegetation borders the scene. On the left side, a cluster of tall trees creates a thick green canopy, contrasting with the bare earth of the field. The right side shows more open land with less vegetation, and a narrow strip of road runs along the top edge of the image. The scene is captured under clear daylight, with bright, even lighting and no shadows, indicating a sunny day. The overall impression is calm and quiet, with no visible buildings or people, highlighting the natural, undeveloped state of the land. The image feels tranquil and still, like a peaceful moment in the countryside.

satellite/000508/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, irregularly shaped land area, likely a rural or agricultural field, surrounded by lighter-colored paths or roads. The central object is the dark, textured field, which appears densely packed, possibly with crops or dry vegetation, giving it a muted, earthy appearance. To the left and top, curved white lines mark boundaries or pathways separating the field from adjacent areas. The overall scene lacks clear structures or human activity, presenting a quiet, unpopulated landscape. The image has a slightly grainy quality, with soft lighting suggesting a cloudy or overcast day, giving it a calm and subdued atmosphere. There are no signs of sunlight, movement, or activity, contributing to a sense of stillness and isolation. The watermark indicates the image is from Google, dated 2023.

satellite/000508/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural landscape featuring a large, irregularly shaped field surrounded by narrow paths and small patches of vegetation. The central area is covered in a dark, textured surface that appears to be cultivated land or dry soil, showing subtle variations in tone and slight curvature, possibly indicating terracing or natural topography. Along the edges, light-colored lines form winding borders, likely dirt or gravel paths, curving around the perimeter and dividing sections of the land. To the right, a circular shape is visible, perhaps a small pond or man-made structure, with a pale, curved feature that might be a road or drainage path. In the upper left and lower right corners, some green areas suggest trees or shrubs. The scene is evenly lit, suggesting a clear day with no shadows or clouds visible, giving the image a flat and neutral appearance. The terrain is mostly open and empty, creating a calm and quiet atmosphere, with a sense of stillness and simplicity. There are no signs of human activity or movement.

satellite/000508/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a park-like area with winding paths and open spaces. At the center is a large, flat, brown field enclosed by a curved white path that loops around the perimeter. To the right, a circular structure resembling a small roundabout or a decorative feature sits at the edge of the path, with a faint dirt patch near it. On the left, patches of green trees and shrubs border the open space, creating soft edges between the natural and paved areas. The main path splits into smaller trails that connect different sections of the ground, forming a network of routes. A small dark spot, possibly a bench or a cluster of trees, is visible near the bottom of the frame. The overall space appears open and quiet, with a clean layout and few visible people or cars. The image is captured under overcast skies, with even lighting and no strong shadows, giving the scene a calm and neutral tone. The grayish white paths contrast with the darker ground, highlighting the deliberate design of the space.

satellite/000509/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, dark brown field surrounded by a light-colored curved road. The field is mostly empty and flat, with no visible structures or features, and appears to be an undeveloped or agricultural area. To the right of the field, the road curves around and continues into a more structured area where faint lines suggest a parking lot or roadway. A small white shape, possibly a car, is visible near the edge of the road. The image has a neutral tone, with no strong shadows or bright highlights, suggesting an overcast sky. The overall atmosphere is calm and uneventful, with no signs of activity or motion. The scene feels quiet and still, like a peaceful corner of a quiet suburban area.

satellite/000509/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a park-like area with curved pathways and open space. In the center is a large, oval-shaped grassy field with a dark, uniform surface, possibly damp or recently mowed. A light-colored, curving walkway surrounds the field and extends outward in several directions, creating a looping design. To the right, the space transitions into a paved area with visible car lanes, suggesting a border with a road or parking lot. On the lower right, a small green patch of trees or shrubs adds contrast, and a faint outline of a vehicle can be seen near the edge. The surrounding area appears quiet and orderly, with clean lines and minimal clutter. The image has a flat, evenly lit appearance, indicating the photo was taken on a cloudy or overcast day, with no strong shadows or bright sunlight. The overall mood is calm and uneventful, like a quiet moment in a public space. There is no visible activity, giving the scene a still and almost empty feel.

satellite/000509/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a small urban park or open green space. The central object is a large, curved grassy area enclosed by light-colored walking paths. These paths form gentle loops and connect to wider sidewalks at the edges. To the right, a paved road runs parallel to the park, with a building visible at the corner of the frame. On the far right, part of a dark multi-story structure and a tree-covered patch can be seen. The park itself appears empty, with no visible people or activity, and the surrounding area has a subdued, organized look. The image is taken in daylight with clear visibility, showing direct sunlight casting light shadows. There are no signs of rain or fog, and the overall atmosphere is calm and orderly. The colors are natural and slightly muted, dominated by green and gray tones. The texture of the grass is soft and uniform, while the paths are smooth and clean. Overall, the scene feels quiet and functional, like a part of a modern city designed for quiet recreation. The space is minimalistic and efficient, with an almost sterile tranquility.

satellite/000510/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area. In the center left, there is a large empty lot with dark soil and a curved paved walkway around it. To the right, a road runs vertically with a few parked vehicles. A house with a sloped roof and a dark shadow is visible on the far right, next to a small yard with a green tree. The scene is simple and quiet, with no people or movement. The lighting suggests a clear day, with natural sunlight and no visible clouds or fog. The overall appearance is calm and uncluttered.

satellite/000510/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a mix of open space and buildings. In the center-left of the image is a large, circular patch of brown ground, likely a park or undeveloped lot, surrounded by a light-colored, curved pavement path. Small trees are visible near the bottom edge of this area. To the right, a road runs vertically, splitting the scene. Along this road, several modern buildings with flat roofs are clustered, including a dark square structure at the bottom right and a lighter gray building above it. A few parked cars appear near the buildings. The surface of the ground outside the central green area is mostly bare earth, suggesting it has not been developed. The image has a clear, bright look, suggesting good daylight and no clouds. The atmosphere is calm, with no visible movement or people. It gives the feeling of a quiet, structured neighborhood, possibly in a recently built or planned area.

satellite/000510/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a small urban intersection with a central open space. In the center and to the left, there is a large patch of bare earth or dirt surrounded by curved white walkways, forming a quiet, undeveloped park-like area. To the right of the space, several buildings are visible—shorter structures with flat roofs, one appearing to have a paved courtyard or parking area. A road runs along the right side, with a white vehicle visible, suggesting limited but steady activity. The scene is devoid of people and has a calm, orderly feel, with the straight lines of the roads and building edges contrasting the soft curves of the pathways. The lighting appears even and bright, indicating a clear day with no clouds or shadows. The overall impression is one of simple urban design, quiet and neutral, with a slightly empty or unfinished character. The lack of greenery or decoration adds to the calm, almost subdued mood of the place.

satellite/000511/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area. In the center, a large dark-colored building with a flat roof sits on the right side of a paved road. To the left of the road, there is a curved white path running alongside a patch of bare earth. A few vehicles are visible on the road near the building. In the background, a fenced area with a light-colored wall and a small structure can be seen. The image appears to have been taken on a clear day, with bright sunlight casting sharp shadows. The overall scene looks calm and orderly, with no signs of active movement or busy activity.

satellite/000511/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with a mix of buildings and open spaces. In the center of the image, a curved road with a light-colored surface splits the scene, running between a large, bare open plot on the left and a cluster of buildings on the right. The open area on the left is mostly bare earth, with a few small trees and a patch of grass, giving it a quiet, unfinished feel. On the right, there is a complex of buildings with dark rooftops and light-colored walls, resembling apartment blocks or individual houses. Between the buildings and the road, there’s a small parking lot with several parked cars, including a red one and a white one. Some green trees are visible near the buildings, providing a touch of nature. The image appears clear and well-lit, suggesting it was taken during the day under bright, sunny conditions. The overall impression is one of a structured neighborhood with a calm and organized layout.

satellite/000511/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area featuring a mix of green space and buildings. On the left side, there is a large, unstructured patch of brown earth surrounded by a curved light-colored pavement path and some scattered greenery. A small road runs vertically along the right edge of the image, connecting to a cross street at the top. To the right of this road, several buildings are visible, including a main structure with a dark roof and a patterned upper section. This building appears to be part of a complex, with a smaller adjacent structure featuring a light-colored wall and multiple windows. The area looks clean and orderly, with neatly placed trees or shrubs lining parts of the buildings. The scene is captured on a clear day with bright, even lighting, indicating good visibility and no clouds. The mood is calm and measured, reflecting a typical modern city layout where open space is balanced with architecture. There are no signs of people or traffic, contributing to the overall sense of stillness and quiet efficiency in the neighborhood.

satellite/000512/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area. In the center, a dark-roofed house stands out, its flat roof marked with small white patches. To the left, a curved road runs alongside a patch of greenery, with a white car parked near the edge. Above the house, a parking lot is filled with more cars, and a pedestrian walkway stretches across the top of the frame. The scene is captured under clear, bright sunlight, casting sharp shadows that define the structures and roads. The overall impression is one of a calm, organized neighborhood, with the orderly layout of buildings and streets suggesting a peaceful urban environment.

satellite/000512/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area featuring a cluster of buildings, a parking lot, and some green spaces. At the center of the image is a large rectangular building with a dark roof and horizontal lines on its façade, possibly a residential or office structure. To the right of the building, there is a parking lot with several white cars parked in marked spaces. In front of the parking area, a row of small trees lines a paved walkway. To the left, a curved roadway runs alongside a landscaped area with grass and a few small trees, where a single car is visible on the road. The overall scene is captured under clear daylight conditions, with shadows indicating bright sunlight. The layout appears orderly and functional, with clean geometric patterns in the streets and structures. The environment feels calm and organized, suggesting a quiet urban neighborhood during a peaceful time of day. The image shows no signs of rain or fog, and the atmosphere is neutral and uncluttered, typical of a well-maintained city quarter.

satellite/000512/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city street and surrounding buildings. In the center of the image, a large building with a dark roof and grid-like windows dominates the view. This building is surrounded by other structures, including a long, rectangular building with a flat roof on the top right. To the left, a roundabout with a circular pattern of light-colored tiles and a paved road leading to it is visible. A few trees are planted along a street that runs between the buildings. On the right side of the image, a parking area with several parked cars is present. The area appears quiet and ordered, with clear lines separating roads, buildings, and green spaces. The lighting suggests it is a clear day, with shadows indicating sunlight from an angle. The overall impression is of a calm, structured urban environment. The photo gives a clean and organized view of the area, showing how the different elements are laid out in a planned way.

satellite/000513/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with a large building in the center. The main building has a dark roof with several rooftop structures, including what looks like a small tower or vent on the right. To the left of the building, there is a green space with trees, and behind it, a parking lot with several white cars parked in rows. The parking lot is bordered by a low wall and a fence made of decorative posts. The area appears calm and orderly, with clean lines and structured layout. The lighting suggests it is daytime, with bright sunlight casting clear shadows. The image feels quiet and uncluttered, showing a well-organized neighborhood from above.

satellite/000513/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring several buildings and a parking lot. In the center, there is a large rectangular building with a dark roof and several visible windows and balconies; it appears to be a residential or office complex. To the left of this building, a narrow street runs vertically, with a few trees lining its side and a small vehicle briefly visible on the road. On the right, a taller structure with a similar dark roof stands adjacent to the central building, possibly a commercial or mixed-use building. Above the central structure, a parking lot with several white vehicles is visible, separated from the buildings by a low wall of patterned paving stones. In the background, there is a grid of open space that may be a park or boulevard. The image is clear, indicating bright daylight with no clouds or fog, giving the scene a well-lit and orderly appearance. The overall atmosphere is calm and structured, typical of a planned urban layout with minimal signs of activity.

satellite/000513/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring a central parking lot surrounded by several buildings. The parking lot is filled with cars and has a patterned design of light and dark square tiles, forming a grid-like appearance. To the left of the parking lot, a curved road leads into the scene, with a few vehicles visible, suggesting light traffic. On the right side, tall buildings with flat roofs rise, their exteriors mostly dark and shaded, indicating the time of day is likely early morning or late afternoon. In the lower part of the image, a larger structure with multiple levels and visible windows is seen, possibly a residential or office complex. A few small patches of greenery, including trees and shrubs, are scattered around the buildings, providing a touch of nature in the otherwise concrete environment. The shadows cast by the buildings are long, suggesting a low sun position. The sky appears clear, with no signs of rain or fog, and the overall lighting is bright but not harsh, giving the area a calm and orderly feel. The image captures a typical city landscape with a balance between built structures and open spaces.

satellite/000514/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with buildings and a parking lot. In the center, a dark-roofed house stands out, surrounded by lighter structures and green trees. To the left, a paved lot contains several parked cars and a patterned walkway. On the right, a light-colored building with balconies is visible. satellite/000777/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large open plaza with a prominent circular feature at its center. The central object is a wide, circular paved area with a dark square structure in the middle, surrounded by a lighter ring of stone tiles. The plaza is mostly empty, with a few people visible near the edges. On the right, there is a curved path bordered by green shrubs, and on the left, a straight path leads toward a building with a reddish-brown facade and a patterned roof. The building appears to have a formal or institutional design, with a long horizontal section above the entrance. The overall scene is quiet and orderly, with clear sunlight casting soft shadows, suggesting a calm, bright day. There are no signs of rain or fog, and the clear visibility gives the image a crisp, clean look. The architecture and layout suggest it could be part of a public or ceremonial space, possibly a government complex or a university campus. The arrangement of paths and structures feels balanced and intentional, creating a sense of openness and symmetry. The colors are mostly muted—browns, grays, and greens—with the central dark square drawing attention as a focal point. The area around the plaza is well-maintained, and the stillness of the scene conveys a sense of peace and structure. Overall, the image presents a calm and organized urban space under clear daylight.

satellite/000778/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, circular stone structure, possibly a historical or ceremonial site. At the center is a square opening surrounded by a dark stone border, with concentric stone rings leading outward. A rectangular structure with columns stands at the top of the frame, seemingly connected by stone steps or a ramp to the central circle. To the left and right, patches of green vegetation and low walls are visible, bordering the stone area. The overall scene is calm and orderly, suggesting a place of cultural or religious importance.

satellite/000778/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large open plaza with a central circular structure. The plaza is paved with light-colored stone and features a round feature with a square dark gray center, possibly a fountain or monument, surrounded by concentric stone rings. At the far end of the plaza is a large rectangular building with a flat roof and a row of small windows. The building has a stone facade with a horizontal ridge and appears to have a covered porch supported by columns. To the left, there is a low green hedge and a small tree. On the right, a strip of greenery separates the plaza from a weaker-distinct area filled with scattered bushes and trees. Shadows across the plaza are soft, suggesting the photo was taken in the morning or late afternoon. The overall mood is quiet and still, with no visible people or movement. The image shows clear weather under a bright but overcast sky, with no fog, rain, or shadows indicating harsh sunlight. The scene feels orderly and balanced, beneath the neutral grey hue of the stone and the muted green of the plants.

satellite/000778/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large open plaza with a central circular feature and a long rectangular building at the top. The center of the plaza contains a circular design with a dark square in the middle, surrounded by concentric stone rings and flanked by pathways. To the left and right, green trees line the edges of the area, adding small pockets of natural color to the otherwise gray and earth-toned space. The building at the top has a long, flat roof and a row of evenly spaced windows or openings along its facade. A few small structures and what appear to be benches are scattered near the plaza entrance. The scene is well-lit, suggesting it was taken during daylight with clear weather, casting soft shadows that highlight the textures of the ground and architectural elements. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with wide open spaces creating a sense of symmetry and balance. The image gives a clean, structured feel, typical of public spaces designed for gatherings or ceremonies.

satellite/000779/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a historical courtyard area. In the center, a large paved square with a circular stone design appears, likely a fountain or monument, surrounded by low hedges and greenery. To the left, a grassy patch slopes gently downward, with a dark shrub near the edge. Along the top of the frame, a long building with a tiled roof and narrow windows stretches horizontally, partially bordered by trees. On the right, a row of weathered columns rises from the ground, part of an old structure. The scene shows signs of age, with flat-colored stone and worn textures. The lighting is even and bright, suggesting a clear day with no clouds, casting minimal shadows. The overall atmosphere is calm and still, evoking a sense of quiet history.

satellite/000779/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large public square with a modern architectural design. At the center of the square is a circular feature, possibly a fountain or decorative basin, with a dark, square-shaped structure in the middle. The surrounding area is paved with light-colored stone tiles arranged in a geometric pattern. To the upper right, there is a covered structure with a flat roof and rectangular openings, resembling a pavilion or entrance gate. On the left, a curved path winds through green areas with small trees and shrubs, creating a contrast with the hard surfaces of the pavement. A few people can be seen walking along the paths, adding a sense of scale to the open space. Some shadows are visible, suggesting the sun is overhead, indicating it is likely midday. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with clean lines and a balanced layout that suggests a well-maintained urban space designed for movement and gathering.

satellite/000779/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a planned public space featuring a large, circular courtyard surrounded by paved walkways. At the center of the courtyard is a dark square structure enclosed by a ring of light-colored stone. A wide, straight path leads toward this central feature, with trees lining the edges on both sides. To the left, there is a body of water, possibly a pond, bordered by greenery. On the right, a long building with a gray roof and visible columns stands at the edge of the courtyard. The building appears to have a formal design, possibly part of a cultural or administrative complex. The scene is bathed in bright, clear sunlight, casting sharp shadows and highlighting the neat organization of the layout. The image has a clean, structured feel, with well-defined geometric shapes and a sense of order and calm. The overall atmosphere is quiet and functional, typical of a designed urban or institutional landscape.

satellite/000780/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a peaceful campus or public space with a wide stone walkway leading through greenery. In the center, a long row of hedges runs parallel to the path, flanked by trees on the left and a large building with a red roof on the right. A few people can be seen walking near the building, adding quiet movement to the scene. To the lower left, a small pond reflects the sky, and a few people stand near its edge. In the bottom right corner, a circular paved area suggests a plaza or entrance. The lighting appears bright and even, indicating a clear day with good sunlight. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with no signs of rush or noise.

satellite/000780/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area featuring a large paved plaza surrounded by buildings and greenery. In the center of the image is a circular, open space with a small structure at its center, possibly a fountain or monument, bordered by a low wall. The plaza is flanked by a wide staircase leading up to a large building with a flat roof and red brick facade on the right side. To the left, dense green trees form a natural buffer, creating a contrast with the hard surfaces of the pavement and construction. A curved walkway runs through the lower portion of the image, leading toward the plaza and connecting to the surrounding area. The scene appears under bright daylight, with shadows suggesting the sun is high in the sky, giving the area a clean and orderly look. The arrangement of buildings and landscape suggests a well-planned public space, possibly a park, memorial, or cultural center. The overall atmosphere is calm and structured, with a sense of balance between nature and architecture.

satellite/000780/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a cityscape featuring a mix of buildings and green spaces. In the center, a large paved area with a curved design leads toward a round structure on the right, possibly a well or decorative fountain, surrounded by a low wall. To the left, a cluster of trees covers a portion of the ground, with a narrow walkway winding through it. Near the top of the image, a building with a long, rectangular roof and evenly spaced windows stands prominently, while another structure with a flat roof and dark edge is visible on the upper left. The area appears to be a public space, with pathways and landscaping, suggesting a planned urban environment. The scene is captured in daylight with good visibility, no clouds or shadows indicating clear weather. The overall impression is orderly and functional, with a balance between built and natural elements. The layout shows careful organization, and the absence of people gives the space a calm, quiet feel. The colors are muted, with gray pavement, green trees, and neutral tones of the buildings. A small number of text labels from the image source are scattered across the picture, but do not distract from the main view.

satellite/000781/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a park-like area with a paved walkway and green spaces. In the center, there is a dark, rectangular patch of ground, possibly a dry pond or a shady lawn, surrounded by small green trees and bushes. To the left, the image shows a narrow path bordered by shrubs and a low wall. On the right, a wide, light-colored pavement extends, with a few faint signs of human activity near the edge. Tall structures like buildings frame the upper part of the scene. The image appears taken on a bright day with clear visibility, as the shadows are distinct and the colors are vivid. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, suggesting a quiet urban green space.

satellite/000781/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban park area surrounded by buildings. In the center, there is a grassy open space with a curved paved walkway leading through it, bordered by dense green trees and shrubs. To the left, a row of low-rise buildings with dark roofs stands behind a narrow path lined with trees. On the right, a larger building with a flat roof and rectangular windows appears, partially shaded by a tall tree. A wide, light-colored paved plaza lies just beyond the central green space, leading toward the main building and featuring a few small structures or benches. The lighting suggests a bright day with clear shadows, indicating sunlight from a high angle. The overall scene feels calm and orderly, with the mix of greenery and paved areas creating a peaceful contrast to the surrounding structures. There are no visible people, adding to the stillness of the environment. The image evokes a sense of quiet urban life, modest in scale but well-organized.

satellite/000781/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city park surrounded by buildings. In the center of the image is a small pond with calm, dark water, partially bordered by lush green trees and bushes. A paved pathway curves around the pond, leading toward a stone staircase on the right that ascends to a paved area leading to a large brick building. On the left, a rectangular structure with a flat roof sits near the water’s edge, while other smaller buildings and dense greenery fill the surrounding space. The scene appears quiet and orderly, with no people visible, suggesting a peaceful moment in the park. The sky is not visible, but the light is bright and even, indicating a clear day with no clouds or rain. The overall atmosphere is calm and reflective, highlighting the balance between nature and urban design. The high-positioned view gives a sense of control over the space, showing how the landscape is shaped for both function and beauty. The colors are muted, with earthy tones dominating the scene. It feels structured yet peaceful, a place where city life meets quiet green space.

satellite/000782/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with trees and buildings. In the center, there is a small open space with green grass and a few trees, surrounded by concrete paths. To the left, there are several houses with flat roofs, and a fence runs along the edge. On the right, there is a larger building with a dark roof, partially hidden by bushes. A curved walkway leads through the greenery, leading to a small gate. The scene is calm and quiet, with no people visible. The image appears to be taken under clear skies, with soft sunlight casting light shadows. The overall impression is peaceful and orderly, suggesting a quiet neighborhood.

satellite/000782/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban residential area. In the center of the image, there is a small park with green trees and a paved path that curves through the space. To the left, several houses with flat roofs are visible, surrounded by greenery and fenced yards. On the right side, taller buildings stand, possibly apartment complexes, with open spaces between them. The area appears peaceful and orderly, with no visible movement or people. The sunlight is bright, casting short shadows, suggesting it is midday. The sky is clear, with no clouds visible, giving the scene a clean and calm atmosphere. The color palette is dominated by green from the trees, gray from the pavement and buildings, and some brown tones from the dry patches of grass. Overall, the image gives the impression of a serene neighborhood, where nature and urban life coexist quietly.

satellite/000782/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with buildings, trees, and paved paths. In the center, there is a small green space with several large trees. A winding walkway curves through the green area, connecting different parts of the site. The ground is mostly covered with concrete and paved surfaces, intermixed with patches of grass and shrubs. The image appears to be taken on a clear day with bright sunlight, casting short shadows. The overall scene gives a sense of a calm and organized neighborhood with plenty of greenery. The layout seems well-planned, with wide paths and spaced-out buildings. The colors are muted, with earthy tones from the buildings and vibrant green from the vegetation. There is no visible human activity, giving the place a quiet atmosphere.

satellite/000783/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a park-like area with a large open space surrounded by trees and pathways. To the left, a long, light-colored walkway runs parallel to a line of green trees, while to the right, more trees and a sloped area with a walkway descend toward a body of water. The overall atmosphere is peaceful and natural, with soft shadows indicating mild sunlight.

satellite/000783/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet residential area with several houses surrounded by greenery. To the left of this central structure, another building with a dark roof sits partially shaded by dense trees. On the right side of the scene, a small body of water, likely a pond or stream, reflects some of the surrounding trees. The area is covered with thick green trees and bushes, creating a natural and peaceful environment. The sky appears clear, and sunlight casts soft shadows, suggesting a bright but mild day. The overall layout feels organized and calm, with open spaces between the buildings and nature. There are no visible people or vehicles, which adds to the stillness of the scene. The colors are mostly muted tones of green, gray, and beige, contributing to a quiet and serene atmosphere. The image captures a moment of stillness, where nature and human structures coexist in simple harmony.

satellite/000783/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet residential area with several buildings surrounded by green trees. On the right side of the main building, a narrower structure with a darker roof extends upward, partially hidden by trees. Below the central building, a row of lush green trees forms a natural border, separating the area from a paved walkway or road. satellite/000784/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a rural village with a central rectangular building resembling a pavilion or outdoor shelter, surrounded by lush green trees and dirt paths. satellite/000784/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a rectangular structure surrounded by green trees and other buildings. satellite/000784/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, old building surrounded by green trees. satellite/000785/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, rectangular building surrounded by trees and other structures. satellite/000785/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, rectangular building surrounded by green trees and other structures. satellite/000786/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, empty concrete structure surrounded by greenery. satellite/000786/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a rectangular structure surrounded by dense green trees. satellite/000787/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, rectangular building with a flat roof, likely a storage facility or warehouse, surrounded by green trees and foliage. satellite/000787/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, rectangular building complex surrounded by green trees. satellite/000787/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, rectangular building surrounded by green trees. satellite/000788/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet outdoor area with buildings and greenery. satellite/000788/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a complex of buildings surrounded by greenery. satellite/000788/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, long building surrounded by green trees and narrow pathways. satellite/000789/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet residential area. satellite/000789/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a campus or institutional complex. satellite/000789/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with several buildings and green spaces. satellite/001012/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a campus or park area, showing a large curved building with a brown roof. satellite/001012/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a campus or institutional complex featuring geometric architecture and open spaces. satellite/001013/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a small outdoor area with a mix of natural and man-made features. satellite/001014/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a paved crossroad at the center, leading to a large open space. satellite/001014/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with a mix of buildings and green spaces. satellite/001014/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with roads, buildings, and green spaces. satellite/001015/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a paved area with a long, narrow structure running vertically through the center. satellite/001015/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with a mix of buildings and green spaces. satellite/001016/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a section of a city, showing a road intersection with surrounding buildings and greenery. satellite/001016/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a paved area with buildings and greenery. In the center, there is a long, narrow walkway running vertically, flanked by trees on both sides. satellite/001017/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a building complex surrounded by greenery. satellite/001081/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet residential area with trees and houses. In the center, a narrow road curves through the scene, bordered by green trees and vegetation. satellite/001196/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a park-like area with trees, pathways, and geometrically shaped green spaces. satellite/001197/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a park or garden area. satellite/001200/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a building complex surrounded by greenery. satellite/001201/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large building complex surrounded by greenery. satellite/001201/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large building surrounded by trees and paved areas. In the center, there is a circular depression or feature surrounded by small green patches, possibly a dry pond or a man-made clearing. To the left, a long linear structure, likely a road or parking lot, runs vertically, with faint markings and a few parked vehicles visible. On the right, a dark, irregular shape suggests a body of water or a shadowed region, possibly a swamp or dense foliage. The terrain appears dry and dusty, with a mix of brown and gray tones dominating the scene. The image is taken under clear conditions with bright sunlight, casting minimal shadows and giving the landscape a flat, arid appearance. The overall atmosphere is quiet and desolate, with little sign of human activity.

satellite/001300/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, open area that appears to be a construction site or undeveloped land. In the center of the image, there is a patch of bare earth with some green vegetation scattered around, possibly small bushes or trees, indicating minimal landscaping. To the left, a concrete or paved structure with a rectangular shape is visible, likely a building or a foundation under construction. On the bottom right, a dark, possibly water-filled space is seen, which could be a pond or a flooded area. The surrounding ground is mostly dirt covered with patches of grass and small plants. The image is captured under daylight conditions with clear visibility and no signs of fog or rain. The overall appearance is somewhat barren and unused, with a quiet and still atmosphere.

satellite/001300/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large open area, possibly a park or undeveloped land. In the center is a patch of brown ground with some green spots, likely grass or small trees, scattered unevenly. To the left, there is a gray, flat section that looks like a paved surface or a parking area, with a white vehicle parked near the edge. On the right side, the image shows a tall building with many windows, suggesting it might be a residential or office structure. A row of dark green trees or shrubs runs along the lower right edge, providing a small natural border. The ground appears dry and dusty, with shadows cast by the buildings and trees suggesting that the sun is high in the sky. The overall scene feels quiet and empty, with no visible people or movement. There are no signs of rain or fog, and the sky is clear, giving the area a calm and slightly deserted atmosphere. The image has a muted color palette dominated by browns, grays, and dark greens.

satellite/001301/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet, open area with a central paved path curving through a dirt-covered landscape. At the center, a circular arrangement of dark green vegetation appears to form a small garden or decorative feature, surrounded by scattered shrubs. To the right, a dense row of tall trees runs along the edge, casting faint shadows that suggest late afternoon sunlight. On the left, a dark, smooth surface—possibly a parking lot or a road—intersects with the scene. The terrain is mostly dry, with patches of greenery providing subtle contrast. The image has a calm and still atmosphere, with no signs of movement or people. The weather appears clear and bright, with soft shadows indicating a sunny day.

satellite/001301/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet park area with a central circular garden feature. In the center of the image, there is a small, round garden with a dark-colored structure, possibly a fountain or sculpture, surrounded by a path and a few trees. The garden is located on a large patch of brownish-green grass that appears dry and uneven. To the right of the garden, a straight sidewalk runs along the edge of the park, bordered by a row of tall, green trees that form a natural barrier between the park and a nearby road. The left side of the image shows a paved path near the edge of the grassy area. The overall scene is calm and still, with no people or vehicles visible, giving it a peaceful and quiet feel. The lighting suggests it is a clear day with bright sunlight, casting distinct shadows on the ground. The atmosphere is neutral, with no obvious signs of wind or rain, and the colors are natural and subdued. The image appears to be taken during the daytime under good visibility conditions.

satellite/001301/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large open park area. In the center, there is a round garden with a small structure, possibly a fountain or monument, surrounded by a circular path. The ground around this area is mostly bare with patches of grass and dirt. To the left, there is a paved surface, likely a parking area or a small field, with no clear structures. On the right side, a line of tall trees runs along a road or pathway, providing a natural border. A few scattered trees are visible in the park, adding green spots to the landscape. The image appears clear and bright, suggesting it was taken on a sunny day with strong sunlight. The colors are natural, with earthy tones dominating the space. The overall scene feels calm and quiet, with no signs of people or activity. The trees on the right side give a sense of enclosure, while the open space in the middle feels expansive. The image captures a simple outdoor area, possibly used for recreation or relaxation, with a peaceful and uncluttered atmosphere. There is no fog, rain, or shadows indicating late hours; the lighting suggests it was captured midday. The park seems well-maintained, though not overly developed. It presents a quiet, functional green space in an urban or suburban setting.

satellite/001302/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet, open area next to a road. On the right, a straight road runs vertically, lined with a row of tall, green trees. To the left, a large patch of bare, brown ground stretches out, with a few small green patches and irregular shapes scattered across it. A narrow, light-colored path curves through the brown area. The scene appears still and calm, with clear visibility and no signs of rain or fog. The overall impression is one of quiet openness, with the natural elements contrasting against the man-made path and road. The bright sunlight enhances the clarity of the image.

satellite/001302/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a mix of greenery and built structures. On the right, a tall building with a light-colored facade rises alongside a wide road, where cars can be seen moving in a regular pattern. To the left of the building, a line of trees forms a green corridor, separating the road from a wide open space with patchy grass and dirt. In the center-left, a circular design, possibly a small park or monument, stands out with its light-colored outline and darker interior. Surrounding this area, a low fence or barrier follows the edges of the open ground. The area looks calm and orderly, suggesting a peaceful part of a city. The image is clear and well-lit, with no signs of fog, rain, or dark clouds. Sunlight appears to fall evenly across the scene, casting soft shadows that indicate it is either morning or afternoon. The overall mood is neutral and grounded, reflecting a typical day in a city environment.

satellite/001302/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area featuring a large open space and a prominent building. On the right side of the image, a modern structure with a flat roof and light-colored facade stands out, its sharp geometric lines creating a contrast with the surrounding landscape. Adjacent to the building runs a straight road lined with dense rows of green trees, offering a natural border between the built environment and the open area. To the left, a patch of land appears dry and sparsely vegetated, with a circular pattern of faint green markings in its center, possibly indicating a planned or incomplete landscaping design. Faint shadows suggest the sun is high in the sky, casting minimal light and creating a neutral tone across the scene. The overall impression is one of quiet functionality—half-preserved nature, half-structured development—under clear skies and mild sunlight.

satellite/001303/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a long row of trees lining a paved road. On the right side of the image, a modern building with a smooth, light-colored facade stands prominently, its edge cutting diagonally across the frame. To the left, bare earth patches and scattered greenery suggest open land or undeveloped space. The trees form a dark, narrow strip along the road, contrasting with the lighter surface of the pavement. The scene is bathed in bright sunlight, casting sharp shadows that highlight the structures and landscape. There is no visible movement or activity, giving the image a calm and still quality. The overall feeling is one of order and clarity, with a sense of stillness in an organized environment.

satellite/001303/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a section of a city, showing a mix of natural and built environments. On the right side of the image, there is a large, modern building with a sloped roof and a dark facade; a circular feature, possibly a skylight or window, is visible on the roof. A long, narrow path or road runs alongside the building, lined with a row of tall, green trees that create a shaded corridor. To the left of the trees, there is an open area of brownish-gray ground, which appears to be a dirt field or undeveloped land, with a circular patch that might be a small garden or sculpture. The scene is captured under clear, bright sunlight, casting sharp shadows and creating a high-contrast view. The atmosphere is calm and orderly, with no visible people or vehicles, giving the area a quiet, almost still appearance. The image has a clean, structured look, highlighting the contrast between the natural greenery and the sharp lines of the urban construction.

satellite/001303/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with a large building and surrounding landscape. On the right side of the image, a modern building with a flat, light-colored roof and a sloped section stands prominently; a circular feature is visible on the roof. The building appears to be part of a larger structure or complex. To the left of the building, a narrow strip of green trees runs along a road, creating a natural border. Beyond the trees, an open, brownish area with patches of grass and a small circular feature—possibly a small park or fountain—can be seen. The road curves gently beside the trees and continues into the background. The sky is clear, and sunlight casts soft shadows, indicating a bright day. The overall scene is calm and orderly, with a mix of natural and man-made elements. The perspective is high, giving a bird's-eye view of the area, and the colors are mostly neutral—beige, gray, and green—contributing to a balanced and uncluttered visual impression. There is no visible activity, giving the image a quiet, still quality.

satellite/001304/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet street corner with a modern building and a small patch of greenery. On the right side of the image, a flat, light-colored roof stretches downward, bordered by a narrow white wall. To the left, a tree-lined sidewalk runs parallel to a road, with thin rows of small trees planted along the edge. A dark green fence and a row of parked vehicles are visible behind the trees. The sun casts soft shadows, suggesting a calm, clear day. The overall scene feels still and peaceful, with little sign of movement or activity. The image captures a simple, everyday urban landscape under bright daylight.

satellite/001304/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, modern building with a distinctive geometric design. The central object is a long, rectangular structure with a light-colored flat roof, angled diagonally across the frame. A circular feature, possibly a skylight or vent, is visible near the lower edge of the roof. The building stands adjacent to a dark, paved surface that looks like a parking lot or roadway. To the left of this area, a row of green trees lines a curved path or street, providing a natural contrast to the hard lines of the architecture. The surrounding landscape includes patches of brown earth and darker soil, suggesting minimal landscaping. Shadows are sharp and well-defined, indicating bright sunlight with clear skies. The overall scene appears orderly and functional, with a sense of quiet precision. The image captures a clean, structured environment, reflecting a modern, utilitarian design without signs of human activity.

satellite/001304/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building with a large flat roof, viewed from above on a clear day. The building occupies the lower right portion of the frame, its gray rooftop featuring a small circular structure near the lower edge, possibly a vent or skylight, and a dark rectangular section that may be a solar panel or air conditioning unit. The structure is angular, with clean lines and a sharp edge extending toward the left. To the left of the building, a paved road curves gently through the scene, lined with a row of small, light-green trees that offer a soft contrast to the hard surfaces of the building and pavement. Beyond the road, the land appears dry and brown, with patches of grass and dirt suggesting sparse vegetation. The overall scene is quiet and orderly, with the stark geometry of the building standing out against the more natural textures nearby. The lighting is bright and direct, indicating midday sun, casting short shadows and emphasizing the flatness of the structure. The atmosphere is calm and functional, typical of a well-planned urban or suburban area.

satellite/001305/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area featuring a large building with a flat roof. The main structure, located in the center, has a light-colored surface with visible seams and a circular element on the left side. To the left of the building is a dark, reflective surface, possibly a parking area or a covered space, with a few parked vehicles nearby. satellite/001305/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, modern building with a flat roof and geometric design, viewed from above. satellite/001305/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a warehouse or large storage facility. To the right, there is a smaller structure with a greenish roof and a few people visible near the entrance. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with no signs of activity or movement. The sky is clear, with no clouds visible, suggesting fair weather. satellite/001306/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city street with a central focus on a large, light-colored building or structure. satellite/001306/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large building complex with a flat roof, viewed from above on a clear day. satellite/001306/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, modern building with a long, rectangular structure and a flat roof, viewed from above. satellite/001307/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a tightly packed urban area with several buildings. In the center, a tall, light-colored building stands out, appearing plain and solid. satellite/001307/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block featuring a group of tall, rectangular buildings. satellite/001307/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with several buildings and a large open space. satellite/001308/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block featuring a tall white building on the left and a green structure next to it. satellite/001308/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring several buildings, a sports field, and a paved path. The overall view is orderly and flat, with sharp edges and solid colors, giving a calm and structured impression of a functional urban landscape. The composition is balanced, showing a mix of constructed and recreational spaces in close proximity.

satellite/001308/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a mix of urban and recreational spaces. The image has natural daylight lighting, without clouds overhead, giving a clear, crisp view of the area. There are no people or vehicles visible, lending a still and quiet atmosphere. The image feels orderly and functional, balancing built structures with open recreational use.

satellite/001309/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a narrow urban street scene. The central focus is a tan-colored building with a flat roof, standing between two taller structures. satellite/001309/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a city street and surrounding buildings. On the left, a tall, light-colored building stands next to a smaller structure with a green roof. To the right of the buildings is a wide, dark green area that looks like a park or playground, with faint white lines marking sections, possibly a sports field. The colors are muted and natural, giving the image a quiet, observational feel. There is a sense of stillness in the urban landscape, with the structures and open space arranged in a simple, functional way.

satellite/001309/H100.tif: This is an aerial image showing a section of a sports complex. satellite/001310/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city street with tall buildings. In the center, a light-colored building with a flat roof stands between two other structures. satellite/001310/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large industrial complex, likely a warehouse or distribution center. satellite/001310/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large building complex, likely a school or community center, with a long, light-colored main structure that has a flat roof and appears to be made of concrete or similar material. satellite/001311/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex with clean lines and geometric shapes. satellite/001311/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, light-colored building with a flat roof, viewed from above. satellite/001311/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building surrounded by paved areas and greenery. satellite/001312/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban building with a dark gray concrete structure and a light gray slanted roof. The overall atmosphere is calm and structured, showing a clean and geometric layout typical of contemporary city design.

satellite/001312/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building and its surroundings. The right side of the roof appears flat and slightly darker, possibly from shadows or different materials. Below the roof, the structure has a grid-like lower level with rectangular openings that suggest windows or openings in the walls. To the left of the building, there is a dark vertical area with greenery, likely trees or shrubs, and a narrow path or road running parallel. There is no precipitation or fog, and the atmosphere is calm and neutral, with a lack of movement or presence of people. The overall scene feels quiet and structured, emphasizing the clean lines and geometric design of the building.

satellite/001312/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a building with a large, sloped roof. The building sits on a flat, open area, with rectangular sections below that appear to be part of a parking or loading zone. To the left, a narrow road runs parallel to the building, lined with dense green trees that create a shaded border. On the right, a smaller enclosed space with a lighter-colored wall and a doorway suggests an auxiliary structure, possibly a garage or utility room. The image shows clear, bright sunlight casting distinct shadows, highlighting the building's geometry and the smooth texture of the surfaces. There is no visible activity around the structure, giving the scene a calm, static quality. Shadows stretch across the ground, indicating the sun is at a low angle. The overall atmosphere feels quiet and orderly, with the clean lines of the building contrasting against the greenery and surrounding paved areas. satellite/001352/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city area with buildings, roads, and green spaces. satellite/001353/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with buildings and roads. On the left side, there are several multi-story buildings with light-colored walls and flat roofs. satellite/001353/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block with several buildings and a quiet street. satellite/001354/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with large buildings and a road. satellite/001354/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a section of an urban area, likely a city or town, showing buildings and roads from above. satellite/001354/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a dense urban area featuring several large buildings and a narrow road. satellite/001355/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city area featuring a large building complex. satellite/001355/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large institutional or commercial building complex. satellite/001355/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large industrial or commercial complex. satellite/001356/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large urban structure, likely a market or transportation hub. satellite/001356/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large industrial building and its surrounding area. satellite/001356/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a multi-story building complex located in an urban area. satellite/001357/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block featuring a large building complex with a flat roof and several smaller structures.
