The overall scene is bathed in bright, even sunlight, casting clear shadows and giving the image a crisp, clean appearance. The atmosphere is calm and orderly, with no visible movement or activity, suggesting a quiet moment captured from above. The design emphasizes symmetry and geometry, creating a sense of balance and structure.

satellite/001404/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern architectural structure, likely a public building or cultural center. The central object is a large, symmetrical building with a light-colored stone facade and a curved entrance at the bottom. Two prominent horizontal sections rise above the main structure, each containing large glass windows that reflect the surroundings. To the left and right of the building’s main entrance, two vertical sections extend forward, resembling towers or wings, and are detailed with repeating rectangular patterns. The area around the building appears landscaped with trees and pathways, suggesting a well-maintained environment. The sky is clear, and the sunlight casts sharp shadows, indicating a bright, sunny day. The perspective from above gives a sense of order and symmetry, highlighting the geometric design of the architecture. Overall, the image conveys a calm and structured atmosphere, characteristic of a prominent civic space designed with precision and clarity.

satellite/001405/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex. The central object is a large rectangular structure with a flat roof, featuring a section of glass windows and a light-colored facade. To the right of the building, there is a group of tall evergreen trees, adding a natural contrast to the urban setting. On the left, a smaller part of the structure with a similar design is visible, connected by a white railing. The image is taken during daylight with clear visibility, showing warm sunlight casting soft shadows on the building’s surface. The overall scene appears calm and orderly, with a neat arrangement of architectural and natural elements. The atmosphere is calm, peaceful, and slightly bright due to the sun’s glow.

satellite/001405/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex located in a densely built urban area. The central object is a large, rectangular structure with a prominent horizontal feature: a long, narrow window or display case containing a series of vertical panels, possibly artworks or decorative elements. The building’s facade is light-colored, likely made of stone or concrete, and it includes a curved, low-walled feature at the base, resembling a small entrance or plaza. To the left, another structure with a grid-like roof pattern is visible, suggesting a covered walkway or parking area. On the right, tall, dark evergreen trees stand in contrast to the hard lines of the buildings, offering a natural element to the scene. The sunlight appears bright and direct, casting sharp shadows and highlighting the textures of the surfaces. The image is slightly grainy, suggesting it was taken from a high altitude or with a low-resolution device. The overall mood is calm and observational, with no signs of people or activity, giving the scene a still and quiet atmosphere. The clean lines and geometric shapes suggest a planned, modern design within a city environment.

satellite/001405/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex under bright sunlight. The central structure is a multi-level building with a flat roof, featuring a large stone-colored facade and a prominent bas-relief sculpture above a covered entrance. The sculpture depicts figures in motion, possibly representing a historical or cultural scene, adding a sense of grandeur. To the left, a section of the building lowers slightly with a curved archway forming part of the main entrance. On the right side, a dense row of dark evergreen trees stands tall, offering a natural contrast to the hard lines of the building. Surrounding the building are open paved areas and smaller structures with grid-like patterns, likely parking or access zones. The sky is clear, and the shadows are sharp and defined, indicating midday. The overall impression is one of order and formality, with the architectural details and clean layout suggesting a public or institutional space such as a museum, government building, or cultural center. The scene feels calm and structured, with a balance between built environment and natural elements.

satellite/001406/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex surrounded by trees. In the center, there is a large structure with a flat roof and a grid-like facade, possibly an office or laboratory building. To the left of it, a lower building with a wide overhang features a long, rectangular window displaying what appears to be a mural or text. The area is partially shaded, suggesting it is either early morning or late afternoon with soft, diffused light. Tall evergreen trees line the right side, creating a natural border. The overall scene appears calm and orderly, with clean lines and a quiet urban atmosphere. No people or vehicles are visible, adding to the stillness of the moment. The sky is not visible, but the lighting indicates no rain and a clear day.

satellite/001406/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex surrounded by trees and open spaces. The central object is a large structure with a flat roof and a distinctive horizontal decorative panel featuring a graphic design resembling figures or text. Behind this main building, a longer building with a grid-like facade stands, possibly housing offices or facilities. To the right of the scene, tall evergreen trees form a dense row, adding green contrast to the light-colored stone and concrete of the buildings. The ground around the structures appears paved, with pathways and open areas suggesting a campus or public space. The image is taken on a bright, clear day with sunlight casting distinct shadows, which enhance the textures of the surfaces. The overall atmosphere is calm and structured, with a sense of order and quiet efficiency in the layout.

satellite/001406/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area, focusing on a large building with a flat roof and a prominent glass facade. The central structure has a rectangular, stepped design with a section extending outward, featuring a glass wall that displays what appears to be a walkway or gallery inside. To the left, a curved, light-colored surface with horizontal lines suggests a plaza or outdoor stage. On the right side of the image, a dense row of tall evergreen trees lines the area, creating a contrast between natural greenery and the urban architecture. In the background, other buildings with flat roofs and structured grids are visible, indicating a developed city environment. The image is bright and clear, suggesting a sunny day with strong sunlight casting distinct shadows, highlighting the textures and forms of the structures. The overall impression is one of a well-organized, structured space blending built and natural elements.

satellite/001407/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area. On the left, a building with a patterned rooftop and balcony is visible, standing next to a tall row of evergreen trees that stretch vertically through the center of the scene. To the right, the trees block the view of a section with smaller structures and a possible pathway below. The image appears to be taken during daylight with soft lighting, suggesting it could be early morning or late afternoon. The overall atmosphere is calm and uneventful, with no signs of people or activity. The foliage is dense and has a deep green tone, indicating healthy growth. The scene feels peaceful and still, as if captured on a quiet day in a suburban neighborhood.

satellite/001407/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a mixed urban area featuring a building complex and surrounding green space. On the left side of the image, a large building with a patterned facade and a flat roof is visible, possibly a school or office building, with a covered walkway or porch area beneath it. To the center and right, there is a dense cluster of tall evergreen trees, forming a dark green canopy. Beyond the trees, a lighter-colored open space appears, likely a park or yard with scattered patches of grass and dirt. A few smaller structures and vehicles are visible in the background, suggesting a functional, everyday environment. The lighting is bright and clear, indicating daytime with no visible clouds or fog. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with the contrast between the structured architecture and the natural trees creating a balanced scene. The image captures a quiet moment in a developed area where nature and buildings coexist.

satellite/001407/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city area featuring buildings, trees, and open spaces. On the left side, there is a large building with a light-colored facade and a broad roof, topped with a decorative wall mural. Adjacent to this structure is a taller building with a grid-like pattern of windows and a sloped roof. A wide road separates these buildings from a grassy area on the right, which contains a line of dense evergreen trees and a few scattered smaller structures. Further to the right, there is a dark open space, possibly a parking lot, with a red vehicle visible. The image appears to have been taken during the day under bright sunlight, which creates clear shadows stretching across the buildings and ground. The overall impression is one of a functional urban landscape, with a mix of architectural and natural elements, neither overly crowded nor empty. The scene feels calm and orderly, with the geometry of buildings contrasting with the organic shape of the trees.

satellite/001408/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a wooded area with some man-made structures. In the center, there is a clearing with patches of dirt and grass, surrounded by dense trees that appear dark and shadowy. To the left, part of a light-colored building is visible, with a flat roof and vertical lines suggesting windows or panels. On the right, a tall red object—possibly a piece of machinery or a sign—stands out against the green and brown landscape. The trees are closely packed, giving the scene a closed-in, quiet feel. The image is clear, with bright sunlight casting sharp shadows, suggesting it was taken on a sunny day. The overall atmosphere is calm and isolated, with no visible movement or people.

satellite/001408/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with a mix of buildings and green spaces. In the center, there is a large open patch of ground surrounded by trees, which appears to be a courtyard or small park area. To the left, part of a multi-story building is visible, with a balcony and windows, showing a typical urban structure. On the right side of the image, a sports field with red and green sections can be seen, likely used for outdoor activities. A small yellow object, possibly playground equipment, sits near the center of the open area. The scene is captured under clear sunlight, casting sharp shadows on the ground and giving the image a bright, clean appearance. The overall look is orderly and calm, suggesting a peaceful neighborhood setting. There is no sign of people or vehicles, which adds to the stillness of the scene. Leaves on the trees are dense and dark green, indicating the season may be spring or summer. The view offers a quiet, structured snapshot of everyday life in a city area.

satellite/001408/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring a mix of buildings, green spaces, and paved surfaces. In the center, a cluster of dense evergreen trees stands over a grassy patch, partially shaded by the surrounding structures. To the left, a light-colored building with a flat roof and multiple windows extends toward the bottom of the frame, casting a long shadow. Above this building, another structure with a grid-like facade appears more industrial in appearance. On the right, a bright red surface—likely a sports court—contrasts sharply with the adjacent green field and small light-colored structures. Near the bottom right, a low blue-roofed building sits beside narrow pathways, while a red vehicle or container-like object rests near the edge of the red surface. The scene is illuminated by bright sunlight, creating clear, defined shadows that suggest a clear day. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with no visible movement or people. The mix of trees, open spaces, and built elements gives the impression of a well-organized city environment, balancing natural and artificial features.

satellite/001409/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a park-like area with a mix of natural and man-made features. In the center, there is a small structure that looks like a shelter or pavilion, surrounded by dirt paths and patches of green grass. To the left, dense trees provide shade and cover a large part of the space, creating a quiet and secluded atmosphere. On the right, a red sports court with white lines and a green playing area suggests a place for recreation. A few long, narrow objects, possibly benches or racks, are placed near the court. The sky is clear, indicating a bright and sunny day without clouds. The scene feels calm and organized, with a balance between open space and natural growth.

satellite/001409/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a school or educational complex. In the center, there is a fenced area with a basketball hoop and a small play structure, possibly a playground or sports court. To the right of this space, there are two green tennis courts set within a red-tiled surface, suggesting a recreational or physical education area. On the left side, a dense row of tall evergreen trees lines the edge of the property, providing greenery and some shade. The surrounding buildings are mostly flat-roofed and made of concrete or brick, with neutral colors. The scene is well-lit, indicating the photo was taken during clear daytime conditions, with no visible clouds or shadows that suggest extreme sun angles. The overall impression is calm and functional, with organized spaces for sport, learning, and nature. The layout appears structured and efficient, typical of educational facilities. The image shows no people or movement, giving it a still and orderly atmosphere.

satellite/001409/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a mixed-use urban area with recreational and built structures. In the center, there is a small open space with a few trees, a paved path, and some seating or benches. To the left, there is a block of buildings covered with dense trees, creating a shaded area. On the right side, there are several red and green tennis courts with white lines, surrounded by a red running track. Above the courts, a larger green field or sports area can be seen. At the bottom, part of a blue-tiled building is visible, and toward the top, a white building with a green roof stands near another structure with a yellowish facade. The image is taken under clear skies with bright sunlight, casting sharp shadows and highlighting the colors of the surfaces. The overall scene feels orderly and functional, with a mix of greenery and sports facilities in a developed city setting.

satellite/001410/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a sports complex. On the right side, there are several green tennis courts with white lines, surrounded by a reddish-brown track. To the left, a long, red and white structure—possibly a bridge or covered walkway—runs parallel to the courts. Behind it, a dark green area covered with trees forms a natural border. There are a few small buildings and open spaces near the center-left, including what looks like a rectangular open field. The area appears quiet and empty of people. The lighting is clear, suggesting a sunny day with no visible clouds or fog. The overall view is calm and orderly, with natural and man-made features neatly arranged.

satellite/001410/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a sports complex. On the right side of the image, there is a large red building with several green tennis courts attached to its side. The courts are arranged in rows and are separated by thin white lines. To the left, a small yellow structure, possibly a shed or pavilion, sits near a paved area with markings that suggest a parking or entry zone. A large red crane stands near the middle, suggesting some construction or maintenance work. Surrounding the site is a mix of trees and greenery, creating a shaded, natural border. The area appears quiet and unused at the moment, without visible people or activity. The lighting in the image is even and soft, indicating an overcast day with no strong shadows. The overall scene feels calm and orderly, with the red and green colors standing out against the darker tones of the trees and ground. The texture of the surfaces—paved areas, court tops, and leafy surroundings—is clearly visible, showing a well-maintained outdoor space.

satellite/001410/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a sports complex with a mix of green fields and red surfaces. On the right side, there is a large outdoor sports area featuring several tennis courts and a running track with a red surface and a central green field, possibly used for football or athletics. The courts are neatly arranged in rows, and white lines mark the playing areas. To the left, there is a more natural section with dense trees forming a green zone, and a small building with a gray roof appears beneath the trees. A large structure with a red and white pattern, possibly a construction or temporary shelter, is positioned between the trees and the sports area. The area is bordered by a paved path or road that runs along the side. The lighting in the image suggests it was taken during daylight, with no heavy shadows or weather effects like fog or rain, giving the scene a clear and functional appearance. There is no visible human activity, giving the setting a calm and orderly look.

satellite/001411/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a sports complex. In the center, there are several green tennis courts with white lines, arranged in a grid on a red surface. To the left, a blue-roofed building sits near a wooden structure and a tall, reddish-red tower-like object surrounded by trees. The area is bordered by green bushes and trees, creating a contrast with the open courts. The lighting is even and bright, suggesting a clear day with no visible clouds or rain. The space appears organized and quiet, with no people or movement visible. The overall impression is one of calm functionality, typical of a recreational area during a non-peak time.

satellite/001411/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a sports complex with multiple tennis courts. The central focus is a large rectangular area with ten green tennis courts arranged in two vertical rows of five, separated by red clay or asphalt paths. Alongside the courts, there are white painted lines marking the boundaries and service areas. To the left of the courts, there is a section with a white-roofed building and adjacent parking spaces with a few cars. A tall red and white structure, possibly a tower or lighting pole, stands between the courts and the building area. There is also a narrow path running along the left side, bordered by trees and greenery. The area surrounding the complex is a mix of natural and developed land, with trees and open spaces visible on the top left. The image appears to be taken during the day under clear weather, as there are no signs of rain or fog, and shadows are visible. The scene has a calm and organized look, typical of a well-maintained recreational area.

satellite/001411/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a sports complex with multiple outdoor tennis courts, surrounded by open green spaces and trees. The courts are arranged in neat rows, with bright green playing surfaces on a reddish-brown ground, and some court lines appear faded from use. To the right of the courts, a portion of a red running track is visible, forming a curved edge along the top of the image. On the left side, a narrow road runs vertically, bordered by a mix of paved areas, vegetation, and a small white building with a sloped roof, possibly a shed or utility structure. A larger rectangular building with a smooth blue-grey roof sits below the tennis courts, partially shaded by trees. There is a cluster of parked vehicles near the building, and a smaller sports area with what looks like a basketball hoop can be seen in the lower right corner. The image is captured on a bright, clear day with strong sunlight casting sharp shadows, suggesting it was taken midday. The overall scene feels structured and orderly, with a sense of quiet activity in a well-defined recreational area. The lush green trees contrast with the red and green sports facilities, giving the area a clean and functional appearance.

satellite/001412/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a sports complex surrounded by trees. On the right, there are several green tennis courts with red surrounding paths, appearing empty and quiet. In the center, a large red structure, possibly a playground or outdoor gym equipment, stands near a paved area with a few small buildings, including one with a blue roof. To the left, dense dark green trees block much of the view, covering a pathway and a low wall. The scene is bathed in bright sunlight, casting sharp shadows, and the overall mood is calm and still, suggesting a peaceful, unused space during the day.

satellite/001412/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a sports and recreational area surrounded by greenery. On the right side of the image, there are several tennis courts with green playing surfaces and red clay surrounding them, enclosed by a low fence. A white building with a flat, light-colored roof sits just below the courts. To the left, there is a network of pathways winding through a dense area of trees and shrubs, with a few scattered benches visible. In the center, an open space contains a rectangular pavilion or structure with a dark roof, possibly a seating area or landscaping feature. The image is captured under clear daylight, with shadows indicating sunlight from the left, giving the scene a bright and open feel. The overall atmosphere is calm and functional, blending natural elements with man-made structures for outdoor use. Trees dominate the left side, providing shade and a natural border to the recreational space.

satellite/001412/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a sports and recreation area, captured on a clear day with bright sunlight. On the right side of the image, there is a large red sports field with multiple green tennis courts, each marked with white lines and enclosed by low fences. A tall red metal structure, possibly a light pole or tower, stands near the center right. To the left of the field, a grassy area with several trees and some scattered benches or benches is visible. A paved pathway runs along the left edge, curving gently downward, with a few parked cars visible along the road below. A large light-colored building with a sloped roof appears on the far left, partially visible. The scene is calm and orderly, with no people seen, suggesting a quiet moment in a public space. The overall atmosphere is clean and structured, typical of a well-maintained urban park or campus grounds.

satellite/001413/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a small urban area with buildings and green spaces. In the center, there is a grassy area with some structures, possibly a sports field or playground, surrounded by tall trees that cast long shadows. To the left, a large light-colored building with a flat roof is visible, while to the right, another structure with a lighter-colored wall stands near a narrow path. Small paved roads connect the buildings and trees, and there are a few parked vehicles near the buildings. The image appears to be taken on a clear day with bright sunlight, highlighting the contrast between the greenery and the built environment. The overall scene feels calm and orderly, with no visible people or movement.

satellite/001413/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a schoolyard area adjacent to a large building. In the center, there is a paved space with a red and yellow playground structure, likely a climbing frame, surrounded by grass and mature trees. To the left, part of a light-colored building with a flat roof and large windows is visible, casting long shadows. A paved pathway runs along the edge of the yard, with a few parked cars. On the right side, a red running track encircles a green sports field, and a white building with a blue roof stands nearby. The trees are dense and provide shade over parts of the ground. The sunlight is bright, creating sharp contrasts between light and shadow across the scene. The objects are clearly defined, suggesting a clear, sunny day. The overall atmosphere is quiet and orderly, with no people in sight, giving it a calm and still appearance.

satellite/001413/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city area with buildings, trees, and a sports field. In the center, there is a patch of green trees and grass near a road. To the left, there are tall buildings with flat roofs and large windows, showing signs of urban life. On the right side, a red sports court with green tennis or basketball courts is visible, suggesting a school or community center nearby. A large red structure, possibly a truck or equipment, sits near the court. In the lower part of the image, a curved road or ramp leads down, with parked cars visible beneath a structure with a grey roof. The area is filled with shadows, indicating bright sunlight and clear weather. Overall, the scene shows a quiet blend of nature and urban development, with no people visible, giving it a calm but structured feel. The neat layout and well-defined spaces create a sense of order, typical of a planned city district.

satellite/001414/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city street with buildings and trees. In the center, a tall, dark green evergreen tree stands out, surrounded by lighter green bushes and a paved area. To the left, a multi-story building with balconies and glass railings is visible, casting a long shadow. A low wall with a metal grille runs along the edge of the building. On the right, patches of dirt and leafy trees are seen, along with a small section of road or alley. The scene is captured under bright sunlight, creating sharp contrasts between light and shadow. The image gives a calm, structured impression of an urban green space.

satellite/001414/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area. In the center of the picture stands a tall, dark green pine tree with dense foliage, creating a striking contrast against the surrounding concrete and pavement. To the left of the tree, a large building with a flat roof and glass facade rises, its upper level showing a patterned design. A light-colored, curved wall runs alongside this structure, with a small shadow masked by the pine. To the right, a paved road curves around the tree, with several cars parked along its edge and another building visible in the background. In the lower part of the frame, an open space with a few scattered trees and a small structure can be seen. The scene is lit by bright sunlight, casting clear shadows and highlighting the textures of the road, walls, and leaves. The atmosphere is calm and orderly, with minimal movement or people present, suggesting a quiet moment in a developed city environment.

satellite/001414/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large building complex surrounded by trees and paved areas. On the left side of the image, a tall, rectangular building with a flat roof and many windows stands prominently. Below it is a wide, open plaza made of light-colored stone tiles, with a curved wall and steps leading up to the main structure. A row of dark evergreen trees runs along the central area, separating the building from a more wooded zone on the right. To the right, there is a patch of green grass, a few scattered vehicles, and what appears to be a train or railway equipment in the far distance. The area has a calm, organized feel, with tracks and pathways forming a pattern on the ground. The lighting suggests a bright, clear day, with long shadows indicating the sun is low in the sky. The overall atmosphere is still and orderly, with no signs of people or traffic, giving a sense of quiet after a day's activity.

satellite/001415/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex surrounded by trees. The central object is a large, light-colored structure with a curved, recessed entrance and a horizontal window section featuring geometric patterns. To the left, another section of the building rises, showing a darker, grid-like facade. On the right, a cluster of tall evergreen trees provides a natural contrast to the smooth, clean lines of the architecture. Below, a paved area extends outward, with shadows cast by the buildings and trees, indicating bright, clear sunlight. The scene feels calm and orderly, with the hard angles of the man-made structures balanced by the soft shapes of the greenery. The atmosphere is quiet and structured, like a well-planned urban space.

satellite/001415/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern architectural complex surrounded by greenery. At the center, a large rectangular structure with a flat roof stands out, featuring a prominent horizontal design element that appears to be a decorative or symbolic carvings. This central building is connected to a wide, paved plaza made of light-colored stone tiles, which leads up to a set of stairs or ramp with a curved edge, suggesting a formal entrance. To the right of the structure, a row of tall, densely packed evergreen trees creates a natural border. In the background, another building with a grid-like facade of windows is visible, possibly a residential or office tower. The scene is illuminated by bright sunlight, casting clear shadows on the ground. There are no people visible, giving the area a calm and orderly appearance. The overall impression is of a well-planned, serene urban space.

satellite/001415/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large modern building complex surrounded by green trees. The central object is a tall rectangular structure with a glass facade and a flat roof, featuring a large rectangular panel on its front that displays a series of images or artwork. To the left of this main building is a wide, open plaza made of light-colored stone tiles, which appears empty and orderly. A curved stone wall borders the plaza on its lower side, and a few small shadows from nearby trees can be seen on the ground. To the right of the main building, a dense group of tall evergreen trees stands, casting long dark shadows. Below the trees, a narrow path or roadway runs diagonally through the scene, with a few vehicles faintly visible. The sunlight is bright and sharp, creating strong contrasts between light and shadow, which gives the image a clear and sharp appearance. The overall atmosphere is calm and structured.

satellite/001416/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building with a large, rectangular facade. The central object is a massive stone or concrete structure featuring a long, horizontal window or display area with a grid-like design, possibly showing artwork or signage. The building’s surface is smooth and light-colored, with a curved edge and a flat roof. To the right, a tall evergreen tree stands, adding greenery to the scene. On the left, a railing or railing-like structure is visible, suggesting a raised walkway or rooftop area. The area around the building includes paved ground and some smaller objects, possibly vehicles or equipment, near the base. The lighting is bright and clear, indicating a sunny day with no clouds or fog, casting sharp shadows. The overall scene appears calm and orderly, with a clean, functional look.

satellite/001416/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area featuring a prominent building with a large, rectangular structure above it. The central object is a white, rectangular platform with a glass-paneled section that appears to display figures or artwork, likely a monument or memorial. Below this structure, a wide, curved staircase leads up to a raised platform made of light-colored stone tiles. On the left side, a multi-level building with rows of windows and shaded overhangs can be seen, while on the right, a tall evergreen tree adds a touch of green to the scene. Shadows stretch across the pavement, suggesting bright sunlight and a clear day. The area appears clean and orderly, with no visible people, giving it a quiet and structured atmosphere. The overall setting feels still and organized, with a focus on architectural design and open space. The image captures a moment of calm in a well-maintained city environment.

satellite/001416/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex surrounded by trees and open spaces. In the center of the image is a large flat structure with a rectangular entrance area featuring a glass facade that shows reflections of the sky and nearby objects. Above the entrance, there is a raised section with visible railings and a canopy, possibly for shelter or decoration. To the left, a series of curved stone benches lead down a wide pathway, creating a sense of order and symmetry. Tall, dark evergreen trees are clustered along the right edge of the image, casting long shadows across the ground. The sunlight is bright, suggesting a clear day, and the shadows indicate it is either morning or late afternoon. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with clean lines and a mix of natural and man-made elements. There is no visible movement or people, which adds to the stillness of the scene. The cool blue tones of the shadows contrast with the warm beige of the stone, creating a balanced visual effect.

satellite/001417/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern architectural structure, likely a public building or cultural center. At the center is a curved, open pavilion with smooth, light-colored stone steps and a low archway, suggesting a place for gatherings or ceremonies. Above it, a long rectangular building with large glass windows and decorative stone panels stretches horizontally. On the left, a smaller structure with a smooth facade and a vertical feature resembling a sculpture or screen stands beside it. The roof of the main building is composed of a grid-like pattern, possibly a solar panel array or shaded walkway. Shadows of nearby trees fall across the pavement, and the scene appears peaceful under bright daylight, with clear skies casting sharp definitions on the architecture. The overall impression is one of clean design and functional simplicity.

satellite/001417/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex with a wide, open courtyard in the foreground. The central object is a curved, elevated platform made of light-colored stone tiles, which forms a semi-circular stage or seating area. On either side of this structure, there are two small, leafy trees providing slight green contrast to the neutral tones. Behind the courtyard, a two-story building extends across the frame, featuring large glass windows and a clean, geometric design. The upper floor includes a balcony or walkway with visible railings. The surrounding area includes more buildings with similar architectural styles and flat roofs. The image is captured on a bright, sunny day, as indicated by strong shadows and clear lighting. The overall atmosphere is calm and structured, with a sense of order and symmetry in the design. The color palette consists mainly of beige, gray, and muted green, adding to the quiet, functional feel of the space.

satellite/001417/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, modern building with a symmetrical design, viewed from above. The central object is a wide, light-colored stone structure with a curved archway at the front, flanked by two tall, rectangular sections that rise vertically and feature large windows with decorative grilles. The building has multiple levels, with rows of balconies and a flat roof. In front of the main building, there is a broad courtyard or plaza area paved with light-colored stone blocks, bordered by a series of low steps or terraces. On the right side, tall evergreen trees cast long shadows across the scene. The left side shows parts of nearby buildings with similar architectural lines. The image is taken in bright daylight, with clear shadows indicating a high sun. The atmosphere appears calm and orderly, with no visible people or movement. The overall impression is one of clean, structured design and quiet grandeur.

satellite/001418/H80.tif: This is an aerial view of a modern architectural structure, possibly a public building or cultural center. In the center, a large flat-roofed area is visible, surrounded by tiered seating that resembles a stadium or amphitheater. On the left and right sides, large rectangular walls stand with glass panels, suggesting windows or decorative elements. A curved, sunken feature, possibly a fountain or garden, lies in the foreground, framed by clean stone steps. The scene is bathed in bright sunlight, casting sharp shadows and highlighting the smooth textures of the stone and glass. The overall feel is calm and structured, evoking a sense of order and quiet modernity.

satellite/001418/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern architectural complex with multiple levels and geometric design. In the center is a large, light-colored plaza with curved edges and a patterned tile surface, leading up to a set of stairs at the bottom of the frame. The main structure above the plaza features a long horizontal building with two symmetrical sections separated by a gap. On the left, there is a row of rectangular windows with dark frames, while the right section has a similar window pattern but includes graffiti or decorative marks on the glass. A railing runs along the top edge of the building. To the left of the plaza, a slanted wall supports a series of vertical panels with a repeating pattern. On the right, a flat, angled surface with several ridges resembles a stepped roof or sunshade structure. Above the central building, a darker section suggests a multi-story structure with a grid-like pattern. The image is taken under bright sunlight, casting sharp shadows that give depth to the scene. The overall atmosphere is calm and structured, with a sense of order in the clean lines and symmetry of the design. The colors are mostly neutral—beige, gray, and black—contributing to a modern and minimal aesthetic.

satellite/001418/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern architectural structure, likely a cultural or civic building, captured under bright daylight conditions. The central focus is a large, open plaza with a curved, multi-tiered stone or concrete seating area arranged like an amphitheater, facing a rectangular stage-like projection. Elevated on two parallel platforms with large glass windows, the building features modern design elements with structured lines and minimal ornamentation. To the left, a lower wing of the structure extends with greenery and a small courtyard. On the right, another mirrored section of the building mirrors the left, creating a symmetrical and balanced composition. The surrounding area includes more buildings with flat roofs and some trees, suggesting an urban or institutional setting. The image has a clean, ordered feel with a neutral light and color palette, conveying a sense of calm order and purposeful design. The overall atmosphere is quiet and composed, with no visible people or movement, giving the scene a still and contemplative quality.

satellite/001419/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex. The central object is a long, horizontal structure with a light-colored stone facade, featuring a large rectangular window or art panel made of vertical slats. To the right of this main section, a smaller roofed structure extends, possibly a covered walkway. On the left, a darker, more irregular shape suggests a different building or a shaded area with foliage. The ground below is paved in light stone tiles, forming wide pathways, and a curved wall or railing is visible on the lower right. A small green tree casts a sharp shadow, indicating bright sunlight. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, typical of an urban or institutional setting. There is no fog, rain, or clouds, and the image shows clear visibility under daytime conditions.

satellite/001419/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex, likely a public or institutional structure, captured from above on a clear day. The central focus is a long, light-colored building with a flat roof, featuring a series of rectangular windows that appear to be part of a covered walkway or entrance area. To the right of this main structure, a curved, elevated platform or balcony extends outward, made of similar light stone or concrete, giving a sense of openness and scale. On the left side, a smaller section of the complex includes dark roofing and vertical fencing, possibly a maintenance area or utility space. A narrow outdoor staircase leads up to the main level, and several small green trees or bushes are placed around the base, adding a touch of nature to the urban design. In the background, other buildings with horizontal window patterns are visible, suggesting a surrounding development. The lighting is bright and direct, casting sharp shadows, indicating midday sun in clear weather. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with the clean lines and geometric layout reflecting a functional, modern architectural style.

satellite/001419/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area with several buildings and open spaces. In the center, there is a large light-colored structure with a flat roof and rectangular windows, possibly a public building or an office. To the left, a smaller structure with a white railing and a green area is visible, with trees and shadows suggesting the sun is high. On the right, another tall building has a curved design and a flat top, with a darker section like a smaller roof or patio. Behind the central structure, there is a larger building with a grid-like window pattern and a wider, roofed section. The surrounding area includes wide paved walkways and small clusters of trees, creating a clean and orderly setting. The shadows are sharp, indicating bright sunlight and clear weather. The scene feels calm and organized, with a structured layout.

satellite/001420/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area. At the center, a large rectangular building with a flat roof stands prominent, featuring a long horizontal window wall. To the left, a green tree area provides a natural contrast to the surrounding concrete. On the right, a curved structure with steps leads toward the main building. The scene is illuminated by bright sunlight, casting sharp shadows and highlighting the clean lines of the architecture. Below, a smaller rooftop with a simple railing appears in the lower left. The overall image conveys a sense of order and calm, with geometrical forms dominating the view. The sky is clear, and the bright light enhances the contrast between the built structures and the limited greenery.

satellite/001420/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area with a prominent rectangular building at the center. The central structure appears to be a mid-rise building with a flat roof and a long, horizontal window array on its upper level, suggesting it may be an office or institutional building. To the left of this building, there are other structures including a taller white building with a grid-like facade and a dark, tree-covered space beneath it, possibly a small park or landscaped area. On the right side of the central building, a large open plaza or courtyard spreads out, with a curved section of what looks like a walkway or ramp. The ground surface in this area is paved in light-colored tiles, and shadows indicate the sun is high, suggesting a sunny day. In the background, another multi-story building with a repeating patterned facade can be seen, partially obscured by the central structure. The overall scene has a clean, organized look, with a mix of concrete, glass, and greenery, typical of a developed city environment. There is no visible movement or people, giving the area a calm and orderly appearance.

satellite/001420/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area with a mix of buildings and open spaces. In the center, there is a large, light-colored rectangular building with a flat roof and a wide glass section on one side, possibly a part of a public or commercial facility. To the left of this building, a taller structure with a grid-like facade stands, surrounded by small trees and greenery, giving the impression of a structured, planned environment. To the right, a wide, paved plaza extends outward, with neatly arranged stone tiles and curved edges, leading toward an elevated series of steps or seating platforms. A few shadows stretch across the surface, indicating bright, direct sunlight and clear weather. The overall scene appears calm and orderly, with no visible movement or people. The contrast between concrete, glass, and green spots creates a balanced yet functional city layout. The scene has a clean and modern feel, typical of a well-organized urban development.

satellite/001421/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city area with modern buildings and green spaces. In the center, a narrow road runs vertically, flanked by structures with flat roofs and a mix of glass and concrete. To the left, a large rectangular building with a light-colored facade stands near a shaded patch of trees. On the right, a lower, wide building with horizontal lines and a long upper platform is visible, along with a paved surface lined with taller buildings in the background. The scene is captured under bright sunlight, creating sharp shadows and highlighting the clean, geometric layout. The atmosphere is calm, typical of a structured urban environment, with the orderly arrangement of spaces and materials giving a sense of quiet functionality.

satellite/001421/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area, showing several buildings and a narrow street. In the center of the image, there is a large building with a flat roof featuring a long row of windows or solar panels, giving it a clean and structured appearance. To the left of this building, another structure with a grid-like facade and balconies stands tall, surrounded by tightly packed trees that provide small patches of green. The ground below is a mix of paved surfaces, pathways, and some greenery. To the right, a lighter-colored building with a terraced design slopes gently down, appearing more open and spacious. The overall scene is captured under bright sunlight, creating sharp shadows that emphasize the geometry of the structures. The atmosphere feels orderly and developed, with a sense of urban design focused on functionality and space. The image lacks people or movement, giving it a calm and still quality. The lighting suggests a clear day with no clouds, contributing to the clarity and detail in the view.

satellite/001421/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with several buildings and paved spaces. In the center of the image, a long rectangular building with a flat roof stands out, its roof featuring a series of parallel glass panels. To the left of this building, a taller structure with a grid-like facade and horizontal sections of windows is visible, its surface showing signs of yellowing or weathering. Below this, another building with a white, latticed exterior and several levels is partially seen. On the right side, a large, light-colored structure with a stepped roof and a flat upper section is present, its surface composed of rectangular panels. Several small green shrubs and trees are scattered between the buildings, adding a touch of natural color to the concrete surroundings. The scene is taken during the day, with bright sunlight creating sharp shadows and highlighting the textures of the buildings. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with the structures showing signs of use but maintaining a clean and structured appearance. A narrow path or walkway separates the buildings, leading toward the central structure. There are no people visible, giving the area a quiet, almost still feeling. The combination of modern architectural forms and restricted greenery suggests a functional, designed urban environment, possibly a campus or institutional site. The image presents a clear, detailed view of the layout and spatial relationships between buildings, with no signs of flooding or extreme weather. Overall, it conveys a sense of quiet efficiency and geometric precision.

satellite/001422/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block with modern buildings and a narrow road. On the left side, a large building with a flat roof and rows of windows stands tall, its surface a smooth beige. In the center, a dark road runs between the buildings, lined with small green trees that cast long shadows. To the right, a lighter-colored structure with a slanted roof and a grid of vents is visible, connected by a thin walkway. The area appears calm and orderly, with no signs of people or traffic. The sky is overcast, giving the scene a muted tone and soft light, as if captured on a cloudy day. The overall atmosphere is quiet and organized, with clean lines and structured design.

satellite/001422/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area with several buildings and surrounding greenery. In the center, a tall rectangular building with a grid-like facade stands prominent, its structure composed of repeating window patterns. To the left, a large flat-roofed building with a beige exterior appears more utilitarian, possibly a parking garage or commercial structure. On the right, another building with a lighter-colored roof features a grid of rectangular vents or solar panels, suggesting it may be designed for energy efficiency. Between these buildings, a row of green trees creates a natural divider, with shadows extending across the paved ground below, indicating that the sun is bright and high in the sky. The scene exudes a clean, organized atmosphere, typical of a well-planned city district. The lighting is clear and direct, with no clouds present, offering a sharp view of the architecture and layout. The overall impression is one of calm efficiency, with geometric shapes dominating the landscape.

satellite/001422/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with several large buildings and a narrow street. In the center is a vertical roadway lined with trees, separating two main structures. On the left, there is a large building with a flat, light-colored roof and a balcony structure on the side, while on the right, a tall building features a modern facade with a horizontal grid of windows near the top. Smaller shrubs and paved areas are visible between the buildings. There is a small white vehicle on the road near the bottom left. The scene appears to be captured during daylight with clear conditions, as shadows are sharp and visible under the structures. The overall impression is of a quiet, orderly section of a city, featuring clean architectural lines and organized greenery, suggesting a well-planned environment. The lighting is bright and consistent, indicating a sunny day with no clouds in view.

satellite/001423/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block with modern buildings. A large rectangular structure with a light-colored flat roof dominates the center, appearing to have a grid pattern of windows or panels. To its right, a taller, partially visible building rises, its facade showing a grid-like design. Below and slightly in front of the main building, a row of dark green trees lines a paved area, possibly a parking lot or pedestrian walkway. Further down, a series of lower buildings with dark, tiled roofs and balconies stretch across the bottom of the image. The scene is captured under bright daylight, with clear visibility and short shadows, suggesting it is midday. The overall impression is one of structured urban development.

satellite/001423/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with several buildings and structures. In the center, there is a large, rectangular building with a flat roof and a grid-like pattern on the top, likely a parking structure or commercial facility. To the left and below, a lower building with solar panels on its roof can be seen, suggesting energy use. On the right side of the image, a narrow street runs vertically, lined with trees and bordered by other buildings, including one with a light-colored facade. A white vehicle is visible on the street, indicating light traffic. The scene is captured in daylight, with clear shadows suggesting bright sunlight. The overall atmosphere is orderly and functional, typical of a developed city environment. The arrangement of buildings and trees gives a sense of planned urban design. The image has a technical and calm feel, with no crowded or lively activity apparent.

satellite/001423/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring a mix of buildings and greenery. In the center of the image is a large rectangular building with a flat roof, which appears to be an industrial or commercial structure. To the left of it is another building with a gray facade and a grid-like pattern of windows. On the right side, there is a smaller structure with a textured roof, likely a parking garage or a service building. A paved road runs vertically along the right edge, with a few cars visible, suggesting quiet traffic. Green trees and shrubs line the area between the buildings, creating a small natural contrast. The image is taken in bright daylight, with clear shadows indicating sunny weather. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, showing a typical city layout without signs of crowding or activity. The photo captures a well-organized part of the city, balanced between built structures and natural elements.

satellite/001424/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city street at night. In the center, a large rectangular building with a flat roof and a grid-like pattern of windows is visible. On the left side of the image, a few parked cars are seen along the street, while on the right, a tall structure with vertical lines appears to be a tower or part of another building. Below the main structure, a block of trees creates a dark green band, separating it from a lower rooftop with grid-covered sections. The scene is dimly lit, with faint light reflecting off some surfaces, giving it a quiet and still atmosphere. The weather appears clear but dark, with no signs of rain or fog, and the overall mood is calm and urban.

satellite/001424/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area featuring several buildings. In the center of the image, a large, rectangular structure with a flat roof dominates the view, its surface made up of uniform panels, some appearing darker, possibly due to shadows or different materials. On top of this building, a metal framework or scaffolding stands out, suggesting ongoing construction or maintenance. To the right, a taller construction site is visible, framed by cranes and exposed steel beams, indicating active development. Below the central building, a lower complex of structures with tiered design and glass facades suggests commercial or residential use. The ground surrounding the buildings is dark and densely packed with greenery, possibly trees or shrubs, creating patches of natural contrast against the concrete. The sky is not visible, but the lighting appears even and soft, suggesting an overcast day. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with a sense of quiet progress as the city expands. No people or vehicles are clearly visible, emphasizing the architectural focus of the scene.

satellite/001424/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring two large buildings and surrounding streets. The central object is a long rectangular building with a flat roof, segmented into sections, appearing to be made of light-colored materials like concrete or metal. It has a simple, utilitarian design, with no visible windows or decoration. To the right of this building is another structure with a more complex roof design, possibly a warehouse or factory, with a darker base and multiple levels. To the left, there’s a narrow street with parked cars, and a row of trees runs along the edge of the buildings, providing a touch of greenery. Below, a lower building with a long, covered walkway or bridge-like structure is visible, possibly connecting two parts of a facility. The streets are quiet, with no signs of movement, contributing to a calm and still atmosphere. The lighting is even and soft, suggesting an overcast day with no strong shadows, giving the scene a muted, subdued feel.

satellite/001425/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large, rectangular building with a flat roof, likely a warehouse or industrial facility. The structure is surrounded by dark green trees on the left and bottom sides, giving it a quiet, enclosed feel. A paved parking area runs along the left edge, with a few parked cars visible. In the lower part of the image, several smaller buildings with grid-like window patterns are seen. The overall scene appears calm and orderly under clear daylight, with no signs of people or activity. The image has a slightly shadowed look, possibly due to early morning or late afternoon light.

satellite/001425/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a city scene showing a large, flat-roofed building, possibly a warehouse or industrial structure, at the center. The roof has a regular pattern of rectangles, likely skylights or ventilation panels. To the left of this building, there is a narrow road lined with green trees and a few parked cars; a white car is visible driving along the road. In front of the main building, a smaller structure with a lower roof and multiple large windows appears to be part of a commercial or office complex. The area around these buildings includes dense greenery, possibly a park or landscaped grounds. The lighting in the image suggests it was taken during the day under clear skies, with no visible shadows indicating direct sunlight. Overall, the scene feels organized and utilitarian, with little sign of human activity. There are no signs of rain or fog, and the colors are muted, with gray tones dominating the structures and dark green from the trees. The mood is calm and quiet, typical of a suburban or industrial zone not in use at the moment.

satellite/001425/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city block featuring a large rectangular building with a flat roof, surrounded by streets and smaller structures. The building, possibly a warehouse or commercial facility, lies prominently in the center, with a dark open area in the immediate foreground that may be a parking lot or construction site. To the left of the main building, a street runs vertically, lined with trees and several parked vehicles. A few cars are visible on the street, and another building with a patterned balcony structure appears to the right, partially overlapping the central structure. Above the main building, a smaller structure with a grid-like design is visible, possibly a rooftop installation or ventilation system. The surroundings include greenery and other smaller buildings, contributing to the urban density. The image is captured under clear weather, with bright sunlight casting subtle shadows, enhancing the textures of the rooftops and streets. The overall atmosphere is functional and utilitarian, reflecting a typical city environment without strong visual distractions.

satellite/001426/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area. In the center and right of the frame is a large rectangular building with a flat roof, appearing gray and segmented into squares. To the left, a quiet street runs vertically, lined with green trees. A white car is visible on the road, and a few more cars are parked along the side. In the background, other buildings are seen, slightly out of focus. The lighting suggests daytime with clear weather, and the overall atmosphere is calm and orderly. The image captures a typical city scene without signs of activity or congestion.

satellite/001426/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area showing a large, flat-roofed building surrounded by a mix of roads, trees, and smaller structures. The central object is a long, rectangular building with a gray roof, likely a warehouse or commercial facility, featuring visible ventilation units and a flat surface divided into sections. To the left of the building, there is a road with cars parked along the side and a few moving, indicating a low level of activity. Trees are planted along the roadside, providing green patches amid the concrete. On the right, lower buildings with sloped roofs and solar panels are visible, suggesting residential or utility use. The top part of the image shows a darker area, possibly a parking lot or shadowed space. The scene is captured under clear skies, with strong sunlight casting sharp shadows, giving the image a clean, geometric quality. The overall impression is one of a structured, functional neighborhood with a calm and orderly atmosphere.

satellite/001426/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a section of a city showing a road, parked cars, and buildings. In the center of the image is a large flat-roofed structure, likely a warehouse or factory, with a grid-like pattern on its roof. To the left, there is a road with several cars driving and parking. On the side of the road, a row of green trees lines the edge. There are also smaller buildings and parking areas with more vehicles visible. On the right side of the image, a tall multi-story building is seen with glass windows and a modern design. The area appears organized but not crowded, with clear shadows indicating sunlight. The lighting is bright and direct, suggesting a clear day with good visibility. The overall scene feels structured and functional, giving a sense of calm urban activity. There are no signs of rain or fog, and the environment appears clean and orderly.

satellite/001427/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area with a mix of greenery and buildings. In the center, a straight road runs vertically, lined with evenly spaced trees and a few parked cars. To the left, a cluster of vehicles sits near a small structure, possibly a bus stop or shed, surrounded by bushes and trees. On the right, a large rectangular building with a flat roof stands out, likely a warehouse or parking facility, bordered by more trees and a smaller structure in front. The scene appears orderly and calm, with no visible movement, suggesting a peaceful moment in the day. The lighting is soft and consistent, indicating overcast weather. There is no strong sunlight or shadows, giving the area a neutral tone. Memories of daily life are hidden beneath the stillness of the view, as if the city has paused for a breath.

satellite/001427/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a street area with buildings and greenery. In the center of the image is a road with a few cars. On the left side of the road, there are several parked cars in a lot, with some trees and bushes around them. A small building with a light-colored roof is visible near the parking area. On the right side of the road, there is a large structure with a flat roof and a paved yard, possibly a warehouse or industrial building. Further to the right, another building with a slanted roof and multiple windows stands adjacent to it. Paved areas with a few parking spaces appear within the complex. The image shows a normal daylight scene with clear visibility, no signs of rain, fog, or sunlight effects. The overall layout suggests a quiet part of an urban or suburban area, with a calm and orderly atmosphere. The scene lacks any bustling activity, appearing peaceful and still.

satellite/001427/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with a mix of roads, buildings, and green spaces. In the center, there is a road running vertically with several cars parked or moving along it. On the left side, a wide road with multiple lanes runs parallel, showing more traffic and marked by white lines. A line of green trees separates this road from a smaller parking lot filled with vehicles, including red and white cars, near a small open space with a white structure. To the right, a large building with a flat roof and a grey facade dominates the view; part of its structure appears to be a covered parking area. Below it, smaller structures with blue roofs are visible. The image seems to have been taken on a clear day, with the sunlight casting sharp shadows, giving the scene a crisp and structured look. There is little detail about people or activity, suggesting a quiet moment in a busy city.

satellite/001428/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with a mix of buildings and green spaces. In the center, a winding road curves through the scene, lined with trees that cast long shadows. To the right, a large building with a flat roof and visible balconies stands out, likely an apartment complex. On the left, smaller structures, including a house with a light-colored roof, are partially hidden by dense foliage. A few cars can be seen parked along the road. The lighting suggests a sunny day, with clear contrasts between light and shadow. The area appears calm and orderly, reflecting a quiet neighborhood setting.

satellite/001428/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban area, shot from above on a clear day with bright sunlight. In the center is a curved road lined with trees and a few scattered vehicles, suggesting light traffic. To the right, a large building with a flat roof and a smaller structure beside it dominate the space, possibly a commercial or institutional facility. On the left, a long row of dense trees runs parallel to the road, with a narrow path between them and a small open field behind. Near the top of the image, two cars are parked beside a larger vehicle, possibly a bus. The scene feels calm and orderly, with no signs of crowds or fast movement. The overall appearance is functional and structured, with shadows indicating the sun is high in the sky.

satellite/001428/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a section of a city, showing a mix of roads, parked vehicles, and buildings. On the left side, a busy road runs vertically, with several cars moving along it. Near the road, a light-colored building is visible, surrounded by a line of dense, dark green trees that stretch diagonally across the frame. Closer to the center, a small lot holds several parked cars, including a bright red vehicle. To the right of the scene, larger buildings with flat roofs dominate the view, one with a grid-like pattern on its top surface, while smaller structures sit below it. The area appears quiet and orderly, with little movement outside the road, and the bright lighting indicates a clear day with strong sunlight. The overall impression is one of structured urban planning, separated by natural greenery and heavy infrastructure.

satellite/001429/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with a large building complex and surrounding streets. In the center, a multi-story structure with flat roofs and several sections stands out, possibly a commercial or institutional building, surrounded by dense green trees. To the left, a narrow road runs vertically, with parked cars and a few trees along the side; a smaller building with a light-colored facade sits near the bottom left. On the right, a taller building with a glass facade is visible, reflecting light. A wide paved area or parking lot lies between the central structure and the larger building. The scene appears bright, with clear sunlight and no visible clouds or fog, creating sharp shadows and highlighting the textures of the buildings and pavement. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with minimal movement or activity visible.

satellite/001429/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a section of a city, showing a mix of buildings and streets from above. In the center and right of the frame, there is a large rectangular building with a light-colored flat roof, possibly a commercial or industrial structure. Below it, a smaller building with a series of balconies or terraces runs horizontally, and some greenery is visible around it. On the left side, a road runs vertically with several cars, including a white vehicle near the top and others further down. To the far left, a smaller rectangular building with a sloped roof is surrounded by trees. The surrounding area has patches of dark green trees and shaded ground, suggesting the photo was taken under overcast or cloudy conditions with diffuse light. The overall impression is quiet and orderly, with little visible movement. The scene is calm and unremarkable, typical of a suburban or loosely developed urban area on an ordinary day, with no signs of activity or weather extremes.

satellite/001429/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a city scene showing buildings, roads, and trees. The main object in the picture is a large building with a flat roof on the right side, which appears modern and functional. Below it, another structure has a light-colored exterior with a long, rectangular shape and possible solar panels. To the left of this, there are several parked vehicles along a narrow road that curves gently. Trees line the path, adding green patches to the urban environment. On the far left, a smaller building sits near more parked cars. The image is captured during daylight with clear visibility, showing no signs of rain or fog. Overall, the scene has a calm and orderly feel, with well-defined shapes and spaces. The lighting is even and bright, allowing for a detailed view of the objects and their arrangement.

satellite/001430/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a parking area adjacent to buildings. In the center, a dark surface holds several parked cars, surrounded by geometry-defined spaces. To the left, a row of green trees stands in contrast to the concrete and asphalt. At the bottom, a light-colored structure with a flat roof features solar panels, suggesting a modern design. Above, a large rectangular building with a neutral-toned facade dominates the image, possibly part of a commercial or institutional complex. The view is clear, with no signs of rain, fog, or shadows, indicating daylight conditions. The overall scene has a calm, utilitarian feel, typical of urban infrastructure. The arrangement of objects creates a sense of order, with defined pathways separating the spaces. The image reflects a functional environment without dynamic human activity.

satellite/001430/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a large industrial or commercial complex. At the center is a long, rectangular building with a flat roof, covered in a grid-like pattern of panels or tiles that suggest solar installation or ventilation systems. Along the right side of the building, multiple glass-paned sections are visible, possibly windows or skylights, reflecting muted light. On the left side, a row of dark green trees provides a natural contrast to the grey and beige tones of the structures. A narrow road runs along the left edge of the image, with a white vehicle parked near the top left corner, giving scale to the scene. Small dark shapes that appear to be additional vehicles are parked near the building’s lower edge. The area beneath and around the structure appears to be a parking or service zone, with what looks like a covered walkway or ramp branching off to the lower left. The lighting is even and bright, indicating a clear day with no visible clouds or shadows, suggesting midday sunlight. The overall scene feels functional and quiet, with a focus on practical design and limited aesthetic decoration. There is no sign of people or movement, creating a still and orderly atmosphere.

satellite/001430/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a large industrial or commercial complex. At the center, a long, rectangular building with a flat roof stands prominently, showing visible structural lines and sections that suggest multiple connected rooms or enclosed areas. The building is surrounded by paved surfaces, with a few vehicles visible near the entrances, suggesting limited activity. To the left, a row of green trees lines a road where more cars are parked, and a sidewalk runs parallel to the foliage, adding some greenery to the otherwise hard-edged landscape. A blue-tinted small structure appears on the lower left, possibly a utility or service unit. The image is captured in daylight, with soft, even lighting indicating clear weather and minimal shadows. The scene lacks motion and vibrancy, conveying a quiet, functional atmosphere typical of industrial zones during non-peak hours.

satellite/001431/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large building with a flat roof. The building has a central section with a series of rectangular solar panels arranged in rows. To the left and right of this section are lower parts of the structure, possibly offices or support rooms. The roof is made of light-colored panels, and a horizontal beam runs across the middle, possibly a walkway or support. Below the building, dense green trees are visible, suggesting a park or garden area. On the roof, two small vehicles, likely maintenance cars, are parked. The scene is illuminated by bright sunlight, casting clear shadows. The overall atmosphere is calm and ordered, with a functional and modern feel. The image shows a well-organized urban structure, typical of a commercial or institutional complex.

satellite/001431/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern building complex with a large rectangular structure and a wide, flat roof. The main building has a grid-like pattern on its roof and is surrounded by some greenery, including small trees and shrubs. To the left, there is a smaller structure with a sloped roof and a few visible windows, and near the center of the building is a small white object, possibly a vehicle or a sign. The area around the main building appears to be paved with smooth, dark surfaces and contains several rectangular structures, possibly ventilation units, along the side. To the right, there is a partially open area with a metal framework or railing. The lighting suggests daytime with bright sunlight casting clear shadows, indicating a clear and sunny day.
