satellite/001444/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a sports complex with several tennis courts. In the center of the image, a series of rectangular green courts are arranged in a grid pattern on a reddish-brown surface, bordered by white lines. Above the courts, a low white barrier runs along the edge. To the left of the courts, a large tree stands beside a long, narrow structure with a light-colored roof. At the bottom of the image, a rooftop with a grid-like pattern is visible, surrounded by dense greenery. To the lower left, a curved road leads past parked vehicles. The area appears calm and well-maintained, with shadows indicating a bright day. The image captures a quiet and organized space where people might go to play sports. The surrounding trees and clear layout give a sense of order and tranquility. There is no sign of rain or fog; the sky is clear, suggesting a pleasant day. The overall view is peaceful, with the green courts providing a vivid contrast to the red ground and dark trees.

satellite/001445/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a mixed-use urban area with buildings, roads, and sports courts. In the center, a large rectangular building with a blue roof stands out. To the right, there is a pinkish-red track surrounding green tennis courts with white lines. On the left, a curved road runs vertically, lined with parked cars and long shadows, suggesting late afternoon light. Smaller structures and trees appear below the main building, and the surrounding area shows signs of a city environment. The atmosphere is calm and orderly, with sunlight casting soft shadows over the scene. The image has a clear, crisp quality, indicating good weather conditions with no visible clouds or rain.

satellite/001445/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a mixed-use urban area featuring a combination of recreational and built environments. In the upper right, there are multiple tennis courts with green playing surfaces bordered by red clay, laid out in a neat grid and enclosed by a fence. To the left of the courts, a low, rectangular building with a gray roof sits near a tree-lined road. The road curves gently and appears to be quiet, with a few parked cars along its side. On the bottom left, a dense cluster of multi-story buildings rises, including a prominent structure with a patterned facade and large windows, suggesting it could be a residential or office block. The surrounding greenery adds a touch of nature to the urban scene. The lighting in the image is natural, indicating it was taken during the day under clear conditions, with bright sunlight casting subtle shadows. The overall atmosphere is calm and organized, reflecting a functional balance between city life and outdoor activity.

satellite/001445/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a school or sports complex. In the center, there is a large building with a light-colored roof, likely a gymnasium or sports hall, surrounded by green trees and paved paths. To the right, a series of outdoor tennis courts with green playing areas and red surrounding surfaces are arranged in neat rows. Beyond the tennis courts, a sports field with a track and a grassy area is visible. On the left side of the image, a more built-up section shows multiple buildings, including a tall structure with balconies and a flat-roofed building, possibly classrooms or dormitories. A curving road runs alongside the complex with several parked vehicles in a lot. The area appears well-maintained, with clear markings and organized layout. The lighting suggests daytime with bright sunlight casting short shadows, giving the scene a clean and orderly feel. The overall atmosphere is calm and structured, typical of a school environment during a quiet moment.

satellite/001446/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with a mix of buildings and green spaces. In the center, there is a modern structure with a flat, gray roof, likely a small commercial or public building. To the left, a curved road runs alongside a tall building with a sloped design and a glass facade. On the right, a red brick building stands next to a green tennis court, partially shaded by trees. The surrounding area is filled with lush green trees and scattered vehicles along the roads. The scene is captured under clear daylight, with distinct shadows indicating a sunny day. The atmosphere is calm and orderly, reflecting a typical city environment with a blend of architecture and nature.

satellite/001446/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a mixed urban area with residential and recreational spaces. In the center, a curved road runs diagonally from the lower left to the upper right, with several parked cars along its side. To the left of the road, a multi-story building with many windows stands, featuring a modern design with a curved facade. On the right, a large red sports field with green tennis courts is surrounded by a fence, indicating a recreational zone. Near the center, there is a single-story rectangular structure with a gray roof, possibly a small facility or utility building. Green trees are scattered around, broken by the man-made structures, providing small pockets of nature. The image is captured under clear daylight, with strong shadows suggesting the sun is high in the sky. The overall scene appears organized, functional, and orderly, a quiet urban landscape with no signs of movement or activity. There are no dramatic weather features, just a straightforward, calm view from above.

satellite/001446/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a mixed urban area with buildings, roads, and sports facilities. In the center, a long curved road runs diagonally from the top left to the bottom right, with several cars parked along its side. To the left of the road, a cluster of modern buildings with flat roofs and balconies stands close together, their concrete and glass surfaces reflecting the sunlight. On the right side of the road, there is a set of sports courts with bright red and green surfaces, surrounded by a low fence. A few trees are scattered along the roads and near the buildings, adding small patches of green to the scene. The sunlight is bright, casting clear shadows and emphasizing the contrast between the structures and open spaces. The atmosphere is calm and orderly, like a quiet city neighborhood on a clear day.

satellite/001447/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with a mix of buildings and greenery. In the center, there is a curved road lined with trees, leading through the scene. To the left, a tall building with a grid-like facade stands near a wide, shaded walkway. On the right, several low-rise structures with flat roofs are scattered, surrounded by parked cars. A large open space, possibly a plaza, lies at the upper left corner. The area is bathed in bright sunlight, casting sharp shadows. The sky appears clear and the scene feels orderly, with a sense of calm activity. Overall, the image presents a quiet, functional cityscape.

satellite/001447/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a city area with buildings, roads, and greenery. In the center, a curved road runs diagonally from the bottom right to the top left, lined with cars and flanked by trees. On the left, a tall, dark building stands beside a lighter-colored structure with a flat roof. To the right, there is a red sports field bordered by a white line, next to a large light-colored building with a flat roof, possibly a gym or school facility. Behind the field, a tower-like structure rises, possibly a crane or antenna. The shadows cast by the buildings suggest that the sun is shining from the upper left. The trees are green and appear healthy, adding a touch of nature to the urban environment. The overall scene is calm and orderly, with no signs of traffic congestion or noise. The weather is clear, with bright sunlight highlighting the details of the urban layout. In the bottom left, a smaller building with a grid-like pattern on its roof suggests a commercial or industrial use. The image provides a broad view of a mixed-use area, balancing infrastructure and green space. Overall, the scene conveys a sense of organized urban planning.

satellite/001447/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area featuring a mix of buildings, roads, and green spaces. In the center, a curved road runs diagonally, lined with parked cars and bordered by trees. To the left, there is a large building with a flat roof and several smaller structures scattered nearby. On the right, a red sports field with green markings is visible, along with a white building and a tall structure that appears to be a crane or part of a construction site. A courtyard enclosed by buildings is located below the central road, with a covered walkway connecting two parts of the complex. The scene is illuminated by bright sunlight, casting sharp shadows that emphasize the geometric shapes of the buildings and the layout of the streets. The overall impression is one of organized city life, with structures and pathways arranged systematically. The vivid contrast of colors—green trees, red field, gray pavement, and blue rooftops—adds visual clarity to the scene. There is no sign of rain or fog, and the atmosphere appears calm and orderly.

satellite/001448/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city street scene with buildings and parked cars. In the center, a dark building with a flat roof is visible, casting a long shadow across the road. On the left, a lighter building with a curved roof stands beside a narrow sidewalk lined with trees. To the right, a curved road holds several parked vehicles, including a yellow car near the bottom. Sunlight creates sharp, clear contrasts in the scene, highlighting the textures of rooftops and pavement. The atmosphere feels calm and orderly, with no people in view, suggesting a quiet moment in an urban setting.

satellite/001448/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area with a mix of buildings and greenery. In the center, a tall, dark building with a rectangular shape stands out, surrounded by other structures of varying heights. To the left, a wide, open plaza covered with light-colored paving stones stretches out, bordered by small trees and a curved barrier. Along the right side, a curved road or pathway winds through the scene, with vehicles visible in a parking area. Trees with dense, dark green foliage line parts of the lower right and are scattered throughout, adding natural contrast to the built environment. The image is taken on a clear day with strong sunlight, casting long, sharp shadows that stretch across the surfaces, highlighting the textures and shapes. The overall atmosphere is calm and orderly, with clean lines and minimal activity visible, suggesting a quiet moment in a well-planned city space.

satellite/001448/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of an urban area with modern buildings and paved surfaces. At the center, a large curving structure, possibly a bridge or overpass, extends diagonally across the frame, casting a long shadow. To the left, there's a wide open space with light-colored pavement and a few trees, giving a clean and structured look. On the right, a series of buildings with flat roofs appear, some with parked cars visible along narrow roads. A dense row of trees lines one side of the road, providing a green contrast to the concrete surroundings. The sunlight is bright, creating sharp and clear shadows, indicating a clear day with no rain or clouds. The overall scene is orderly and quiet, with no visible people or traffic, making it feel calm and uncluttered. The construction style suggests a contemporary city designed for function and space.

satellite/001449/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a city area with buildings and paved surfaces. In the center, a tall dark structure stands out, casting a long shadow across the ground. To the left, there are steps made of light-colored stones and a curved wall that follows the edge of the area. Green trees grow along the left side, adding a touch of nature to the urban scene. On the right, a modern building with a grid-like pattern is partially visible. The ground is mostly flat and made of tile or stone, and the sun is bright, creating strong shadows and lighting up the scene clearly. The overall impression is clean and orderly, with a sense of calm in the quiet cityscape.

satellite/001449/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban architectural complex. In the center of the frame, a large building with a curved, light-colored facade stands out, featuring a series of wide steps leading up to its entrance. To the left of this building, a circular structure with a patterned design is visible, possibly part of a plaza or fountain area. A tall, thin tree stands near the steps, casting a long shadow across the pavement. On the right, a vertical section of the complex shows a patterned wall made of dark, rectangular tiles. Behind this wall, a large evergreen tree brings a touch of green to the scene. Another building with a grid-like roof appears in the lower right corner, suggesting a functional or commercial use. The sunlight is bright, creating sharp contrasts between light and shadow, which emphasizes the clean lines and geometric shapes of the structures. The overall atmosphere is quiet and orderly, with no signs of people or vehicles. The lighting is crisp and the image is clear, suggesting it was taken on a sunny day with good visibility. The composition highlights the modern design and symmetry of the urban environment.

satellite/001449/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban plaza surrounded by buildings. In the center of the image is a large open space with light-colored stone paving and a circular design on the ground, possibly a fountain or monument. A series of tiered steps or seating areas is visible to the left, flanked by tall, dark green trees that cast long shadows. To the right, a curved section of road or walkway runs alongside more trees and a multi-story building with a scaffolding-like facade. A slanted wall or barrier runs along the right side, separating the plaza from the road. Further up, a building with a large decorative sculpture is visible. The scene is lit by bright sunlight, creating sharp contrasts between light and shadow. The atmosphere is calm and orderly, with no people visible. The overall impression is one of clean, structured design in a city environment.

satellite/001450/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a spacious courtyard with geometric stone patterns and a large curved structure. In the center, there is a tall, narrow tree with green leaves casting a shadow on the light-colored floor. To the left, a series of dark, rectangular benches are arranged in neat rows, leading up to the curved design. On the right, a sunlit wall reflects bright light, with a small bush and a dark alley beyond. The scene feels calm and ordered, with strong shadows suggesting bright, clear sunlight. The overall mood is peaceful and structured, with a quiet, open atmosphere.

satellite/001450/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern architectural structure, likely a public building or plaza. In the center is a large, flat, gray-toned area with a geometric pattern and curved edges, possibly a courtyard or open space surrounded by steps or benches. On the left side of the image, dark rectangular sections, resembling seating or architectural elements, align neatly in rows, leading down toward the main area. On the right, there is a taller structure with vertical lines, possibly a modern tower, alongside green, dense trees that add contrast to the built environment. A small vehicle is visible near the top right, suggesting some nearby movement. The scene is lit by sunlight that casts long shadows across the surface, indicating a clear day with bright weather. The overall tone is structured and clean, giving the impression of order and quiet functionality. The design shows a blend of natural and man-made elements, with the trees providing texture against the stark, smooth surfaces. There is no sign of people, which adds to the stillness of the scene.

satellite/001450/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban plaza surrounded by tall buildings. In the center, a large circular design with a detailed pattern lies on a paved surface, framed by a series of smooth, rounded steps that lead up to a slightly elevated platform. The steps are arranged symmetrically, creating a decorative, tiered look that draws the eye toward the middle. On either side of the central feature, tall evergreen trees stand in narrow rows, adding green accents to the otherwise gray and beige surroundings. To the left, a series of neat rectangular planters run along the edge of the space. On the right, a building with a slatted rooftop structure casts long shadows across the plaza, suggesting bright daylight. The sunlight is strong, casting clear shadows that define the edges of structures and objects. The overall look is orderly and clean, with a sense of geometric precision. The atmosphere feels calm and structured, reflecting a well-planned public space in a city environment.

satellite/001451/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a formal outdoor seating area, possibly part of a park or public plaza. In the center, rows of dark wooden benches are arranged in a semi-circle facing a light-colored stone wall with an arched top. The wall has horizontal stone patterns and casts a shadow over the seating. To the left and right, tall green trees stand upright, framing the structure on both sides. The ground below is covered with lighter stone tiles, and a curved walkway or entrance arch is visible at the bottom. The scene is lit by bright sunlight, creating sharp shadows and highlighting the natural textures of the stone and plants. The atmosphere is calm and structured, suggesting a peaceful urban space designed for gatherings or relaxation.

satellite/001451/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern architectural space, likely a public plaza or courtyard. At the center is a large, symmetrical structure featuring a curved, tiered design with steps leading down into a lower level. The structure is made of light-colored stone or concrete, and its center has a circular, raised platform with a decorative pattern. On either side of the central structure are dark rectangular openings or ledges, possibly for seating or display. Green trees or shrubs are planted along the sides, adding texture and contrast. To the right, a tall, shaded vertical structure stands adjacent to the main feature, while the left side appears open, with more greenery and a smooth, light-colored surface. The ground is paved in large, uniform tiles. The lighting is bright and even, suggesting a sunny day with clear skies, casting sharp shadows from the surrounding buildings. The atmosphere is calm and structured, with a clean, minimalistic feel.

satellite/001451/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern architectural space, likely a public plaza or courtyard in an urban setting. At the center is a circular stone feature with a textured pattern, resembling a fountain or decorative basin, surrounded by concentric rings of darker stone. Radiating outward from the circle are tiered, stepped arrangements of rectangular stone blocks, forming ascending levels that create a ziggurat-like design. These steps are flanked on both sides by tall, dark green trees forming symmetrical rows that add depth and structural balance to the layout. The entire area is built with light-colored stone tiles laid in straight lines, contributing to a clean and orderly look. Above, a portion of a building with large glass windows and decorative details is visible at the top of the frame, suggesting a grand civic or institutional structure. The sky is bright, with clear sunlight casting sharp shadows, highlighting the textures and angles of the design. The scene has a quiet and formal atmosphere, evoking a sense of calm monumentality.

satellite/001452/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a historic building with architectural details and surrounding greenery. At the center, a large arched structure with tiered stone steps leads up to a flat roofed section, possibly a clock tower or entrance. The walls are made of light-colored stone, marked with shadows from an overhead sun. To the left, a tall dark green tree stands near a narrow structure, and on the right, the patterned stone balcony lines the edge of the building. The ground below features a circular design, possibly a plaza, with dark paving that contrasts with the lighter stone. The scene is captured under bright sunlight, giving crisp details and long shadows. The atmosphere is calm and orderly, showing a place of quiet dignity, standing solemnly in its setting.

satellite/001452/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a quiet urban plaza with a symmetrical design, captured under bright, clear sunlight. At the center of the image is a large, circular stone feature, possibly a fountain or public water display, surrounded by a wide, light-colored paved area made of rectangular tiles. Leading toward this central feature is a staircase made of dark stone blocks, arranged in tiers and giving the impression of a modern architectural element. On the left side of the plaza stands a tall, light-colored building with a flat roof, its facade structured with horizontal lines. Dark green trees are scattered around the plaza, their rounded shapes contrasting with the geometric patterns of the architecture. On the right side, another structure with a curved roof edge appears, possibly a covered walkway or seating area. The entire scene is calm and orderly, with no people visible, emphasizing clean lines and open space. The bright sunlight casts short, sharp shadows, enhancing the clarity of the design and giving the area a crisp, warm feel. The overall atmosphere is one of quiet functionality, like a peaceful, well-maintained civic space.

satellite/001452/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban courtyard. In the center, a large circular feature made of stone is surrounded by a symmetrical arrangement of steps and benches, forming a public gathering space. The steps are arranged in a fan shape, leading upward from the circle toward a curved stone wall at the far end, which appears to be part of a larger building with large windows and decorative panels. On either side of the courtyard, tall green trees line the walkways, providing shade and a touch of nature. To the left, a tall structure with a rooftop canopy stands in contrast to the low, open design of the courtyard. The ground is paved with light-colored stone tiles, creating a clean and orderly look. The scene is bathed in bright daylight, with clear shadows indicating strong overhead sunlight. The overall atmosphere is calm and structured, suggesting a well-planned space designed for rest and social interaction within a city environment. The design feels balanced and functional, blending architecture and greenery in a peaceful and inviting way.

satellite/001453/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban space, featuring a broad plaza with light-colored stone tiles. At the center stands a tall, dark green tree, casting a long shadow across the pavement, suggesting bright sunlight in the midday. To the right, a set of wide, elegant steps leads up to a curved, light-colored wall, possibly part of a public building or sculpture. On the left, a portion of a white structure with railings is visible, surrounded by scattered greenery. The area appears quiet and orderly, with clean lines and open space. The light and shadows create contrast, emphasizing the geometry of the design. The overall impression is calm and structured, suggestive of a well-maintained public square or cultural site.

satellite/001453/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban plaza with clean lines and structured design. In the center, a wide stone walkway stretches upward, bordered by curved railings and leading toward a large rectangular building with light-colored walls. To the left, a narrow strip of greenery with small trees and shrubs runs alongside a white fence and low-rise buildings, creating a calm contrast to the geometric layout. On the right, a semi-circular architectural feature with tiered steps frames a central circular patch of patterned paving, resembling a fountain or sculpture base. Several tall, dark trees cast long shadows across the walkway, suggesting a bright and clear day. The sky is not visible, but the sharp shadows indicate strong sunlight. The scene has a peaceful and orderly feel, with open, uncluttered spaces and a balanced mix of natural and built elements. The overall impression is one of quiet urban planning, with clean aesthetics and functional design.

satellite/001453/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban plaza surrounded by tall buildings. In the center, there is a large open space paved with light-colored stone tiles, featuring a circular design with a raised inner circle and concentric patterns. To the right, a multi-tiered seating area made of dark stone steps is arranged in a curved shape, forming a small amphitheater-like structure. On the left, the image shows two modern buildings with white railings and balconies, and a narrow strip of greenery with trees and bushes runs between the buildings and the plaza. The overall layout appears clean and structured, with the sunlight creating sharp shadows that emphasize the geometric shapes of the architecture. The weather seems clear and sunny, with bright light casting defined shadows, highlighting the clean lines and organized design of the area. The scene feels calm and orderly, with no people visible, contributing to a sense of quiet urban planning.

satellite/001454/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a residential area with several buildings and green spaces. On the left, a multi-story building with white railings and dark windows stands near a slope covered with trees and shrubs. A small section of a flat roof and a staircase are also visible. To the right, a tall wall with a textured cream surface runs vertically, partially casting a shadow. Near the wall, a dark, dense tree provides contrast to the lighter structures. The scene is bathed in bright daylight, with no clouds in the sky, creating clear shadows and a calm, orderly atmosphere. The overall impression is quiet and structured, with a mix of natural and built elements.

satellite/001454/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area, showing a mix of buildings, walkways, and green spaces. On the left side, there are several multi-story buildings with flat roofs and balconies, surrounded by patches of green trees and shrubs. A narrow pathway runs through the middle, separating these buildings from a wide, open plaza on the right. The plaza has a patterned stone surface and is lined with tall trees casting shadows, suggesting a sunny day with clear skies. The architecture features clean lines and contemporary design. On the right edge, part of a curved structure—possibly a fountain or monument—is visible, along with steps descending into a landscaped area. The overall scene appears calm and orderly, with no people visible, giving it a quiet and structured feel. The bright sunlight highlights textures in the pavement and the foliage, creating a sense of openness and clarity.

satellite/001454/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban plaza surrounded by buildings. In the center of the image, a wide, light-colored walkway stretches vertically, leading the eye through the scene. To the left, a multi-story building with a grid-like facade and several balconies stands prominently, its structure appearing orderly and functional. Adjacent to it, a smaller structure with a dark roof is partially visible. On the right side, the plaza continues with a light-colored paved area that includes a curved walkway and some small trees and shrubs planted in narrow strips. A large circular design is visible at the bottom right, suggesting a decorative feature or gathering space. The buildings and open areas are bathed in bright sunlight, indicating a clear day. The shadows of trees and structures fall sharply to the right, emphasizing the midday light. The overall impression is that of a clean, well-planned public space, blending architectural design with greenery in a bustling city environment. The scene feels calm and structured, with no visible people or movement, giving it a quiet and orderly atmosphere.

satellite/001455/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban development. In the center, a rectangular building with a light-colored grid-like facade stands out, featuring a layered design and a flat roof. To the right, a tall block with vertical lines and a smooth surface appears alongside greenery, including trees and shrubs that add a natural contrast. On the left side, a low structure with solar panels rests on a darker area, possibly a parking lot or shadowed ground. The scene is bathed in bright sunlight, casting sharp shadows and giving the structures a crisp look. The overall atmosphere is clean and orderly, reflecting a well-planned and contemporary city environment.

satellite/001455/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area featuring a tall building with a distinctive open-grid structure on its upper levels, set amidst other high-rise buildings. The structure has a rectangular shape with horizontal slats that create a pattern across its facade, suggesting it may be part of a residential or commercial complex. To the left, a row of darker rooftops and balconies extends along the edge of the scene, while to the right, a wide, paved walkway runs vertically, hinting at pedestrian access. Small green patches with trees and shrubs separate the buildings and walkway, offering a touch of nature among the concrete and glass. The image is taken during bright daylight, with strong sunlight casting sharp shadows, indicating a clear and sunny day. The overall look is orderly and precise, reflecting a planned city environment. The architecture and layout suggest a developed, densely built area, possibly a business or mixed-use district. The atmosphere is calm and structured, with no visible people or movement, emphasizing the geometric clarity and neat arrangement of the space.

satellite/001455/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area with buildings and paved walkways. In the center, there is a multi-level structure with glass panels and open balconies, possibly a residential or office building. To the left of the central structure, there are lower buildings with rectangular windows and flat roofs, some showing balconies with metal railings. On the right side of the image, a wide, light-colored walkway runs vertically, flanked by small green plants and trees planted in patches of soil. A taller building with glass windows is visible at the top right corner, and the lower part of the image contains a dark-colored section that might be a parking area or shadowed space. The scene is captured under clear, bright daylight with strong sunlight, creating sharp shadows and highlighting the textures of the surfaces. The overall impression is clean and structured.

satellite/001456/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern multi-story building with a distinctive overhanging structure. The central object is a large, boxy building with a light-colored facade and a grid-like pattern of vertical columns or railings on its side. To the left, there is a covered walkway or platform with glass panels, while to the right, green trees and shrubs are visible along the edge of the property. The ground below appears dark, possibly a parking area or shadowed space. The scene is captured in clear daylight with no visible weather effects like rain or fog. The overall setting looks urban and functional, with a clean, organized layout and minimal visual clutter. The image gives a calm sense of order and structure.

satellite/001456/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area with a mix of buildings and paved surfaces. In the center, a structure with a white grid-like framework stands out, possibly part of a rooftop or an open-air walkway, supported by a set of stairs. To the left, several flat-roofed buildings with visible window patterns line up in a row, showing signs of residential or commercial use. A dark green strip of trees and shrubs runs along the lower left side, offering a natural contrast to the hard surfaces. On the right, a wide, light-colored pavement stretches vertically, likely a sidewalk or plaza area. The image is taken from directly above, capturing the geometry of the scene with sharp clarity. There is no visible movement or people, giving the space a still and quiet appearance. The lighting is even, suggesting a bright day with little cloud cover. No rain or fog is present. The colors are mostly neutral—grays, whites, and greens—contributing to a calm and functional atmosphere. Overall, the space feels structured and orderly, reflecting the organized layout typical of city planning.

satellite/001456/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area with multiple buildings and structures. The central object is a complex of connected buildings with flat roofs and lattice-like balconies, featuring rows of windows and railings. The buildings appear to be made of concrete and glass, with a mix of open and enclosed spaces. To the left, there are more linear structures, possibly housing or offices, with a layered appearance and repeating window patterns. On the right, a wide paved walkway or plaza stretches outward, bordered by a small green space with plants and shrubs. In the background, more buildings are visible, including one with a metal security fence. The image is taken during daylight with clear visibility and no clouds, indicating a sunny day. The scene has a clean, organized look, showing a modern city environment with structured design and minimal natural elements. The lack of people or vehicles gives a sense of stillness and quiet.

satellite/001457/H80.tif: This is an aerial image of a large urban structure, possibly a multi-level parking garage or a transportation facility. In the center, there is a long platform or walkway with a metal railing, supported by concrete pillars. To the left, several rectangular sections appear to be open parking areas with grid-like metal roofs. On the right, a series of vertical metal frames possibly support escalators or elevators leading to different floors. A wide, flat covered area runs along the lower part of the image, shaded and dark. The surrounding spaces are built up with solid concrete and steel, giving the scene a utilitarian look. The image appears to be taken under overcast lighting, with muted colors and no strong shadows. The atmosphere is quiet and impersonal, characteristic of a functional city infrastructure piece.

satellite/001457/H90.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban area featuring a large building complex. In the center of the image, there is a multi-level structure with a covered walkway supported by pillars and a grid-like roof system that allows light to filter through. The building appears to be made of concrete and glass, with clean lines and an organized design. To the left, there is a smaller, dark-colored building with a sloped roof, while to the right, a partially open structure with vertical railings and a similar roof pattern is visible. Behind the main building, a row of tall trees provides a natural contrast to the man-made environment. The scene is captured during daylight, with clear visibility and no signs of fog, rain, or clouds. The overall atmosphere is calm and functional, without any visible people or traffic, giving the impression of a quiet section of a developed city. The bright lighting highlights the textures of the surfaces and the structured layout of the area.

satellite/001457/H100.tif: This is an aerial image of a modern urban construction site, captured under bright sunlight. In the center of the frame is a large, partially built structure with a flat roof and exposed concrete beams. Several sections of the building are covered with protective white tarping, and a series of rectangular, grid-like openings suggest ventilation or window placements. To the right, a finished high-rise building with repeating balconies and large glass panels stands in contrast, while a lower structure on the left shows more open space with visible stage-like platforms. A narrow pathway runs beneath the construction area, lined with trees and a few small shrubs. The surrounding area is a mix of other buildings and paved surfaces, with a car visible in the upper left corner. The image has sharp contrasts due to strong shadows, giving a sense of organized chaos typical of a developing cityscape.
